(21, '231MOFTDJ8CW', 23, 11, 19, 'Jordana Forever Flawless Pressed Powder', '<p> </p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Medium coverage</li>\r\n<li>Lightweight feel</li>\r\n<li>Controls shine</li>\r\n<li>Blurs the look of flaws</li>\r\n<li>Suitable for all skin types</li>\r\n<li>Mirror and puff included</li>\r\n<li>Made in China</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Flawless face = flawless life! Forever Flawless Powder blends easily onto skin and is never chalky or cakey, so you always look fresh and natural. Blur the look of flaws and control shine for hours! Go on and get flawless!', '<p>Talc, Mica, Kaolin, Magnesium Stearate, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Dimethicone, 2-Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin, Fragrance (Parfum). </p>\r\n<p>+/-May Contain: Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Red 6 Lake (CI 15850).</p>', '<p>Choose a shade of Forever Flawless Face Powder that is closest to your natural skin tone. Use the included puff to pick up the right amount of powder. Apply on areas prone to shine and wherever skin tone is uneven.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Tip: For lighter coverage, apply with a powder brush. Once you’ve applied the rest of your makeup, seal in your look with a second swipe of Forever Flawless Face Powder.</p>', '1190.00', '0.00', 6, 20, '', 'Forever Flawless Pressed Powder', '', 'FlawlessPressed', 'Forever Flawless Pressed Powder', 16, 0, '2020-05-26 17:29:37', 0),
(23, 'PET-0216', 1, 41, 31, 'Petal Fresh Botanicals White Radiance Daily Facial Wash Pineapple + Watermelon', '<ul>\r\n<li>Deep Cleansing</li>\r\n<li>With Fairness Technology</li>\r\n<li>Paraben, Phthalate, Sulfate &amp; Color-Free</li>\r\n<li>Cruelty-Free</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>Petal Fresh White Radiance Daily Facial Wash</p>\r\n<p>Petal Fresh Deep Cleansing Daily Facial Wash is a fruity treat for skin. Natural Pineapple and Watermelon are effective deep cleansers working to remove make up and eliminate unwanted dirt and oil from pores. Formulated with our Petal Fresh Fairness Technology, this product provides excellent results over time to lighten the signs of sun damage and hyper-pigmentation. The perfect first step in your mightily cleansing routine.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Suggested Use</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Massage onto damp skin of face and neck. Rinse thoroughly and pat dry.</p>\r\n<h3><strong>Other Ingredients</strong></h3>\r\n<p>Aqua (water), cocamidopropyl betaine, ammonium lauryl sulfate, sodium lauroyl sarcosinate, polysorbate 20, kojic dipalmitate, *citrullus lanatus (watermelon) fruit extract, *ananas sativus (pineapple) fruit extract, sodium hydroxide, xanthan gum, dehydroacetic acid, benzyl alcohol, sodium chloride, parfum (fragrance). *Certified organic ingredients. Certified by stellar certification services.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '', '1590.00', '0.00', 6, 4, '', 'Facial Wash', '', 'FacialWashpetalfresh', 'Facial Wash', 11, 0, '2020-05-27 12:37:45', 0),
(32, '2508', 1, 146, 29, 'PALLADIO HERBAL LIP SLIX - Seductive Pink', '<p><span style=\"white-space: pre;\" data-slate-fragment=\"\">A long-wear gloss in the form of a thick crayon, these nifty vitamin-enriched treats are handy and super affordable when compared to department store rivals. 12 beautiful shades glide on with ease and creamy, pigmented sticks combine palm-sized convenience with an emollient-filled formula that won’t dry out the lips</span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '990.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', '', '', '', '', 3, 0, '2020-05-27 14:29:27', 0),
