(67, 'NU-2204', 1, 48, 27, 'All-in-1 Acne Control Daily Scrub', '<p>Finally, a multi-tasking daily exfoliating scrub that gets acne\'s past, present and future under control for consistently clearer, healthier looking skin.</p>\r\n<p>This daily face scrub contains a powerful combination of ingredients for acne-prone skin that work together to clear up the three phases of a breakout, without over-drying. Formulated with gentle exfoliators, this scrub smooths away rough skin, and reduces the look of past acne marks. Maximum-strength salicylic acid acne-fighting medicine powerfully clears present breakouts and fights future budding acne before it emerges.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', '', '', '4200.00', '0.00', 6, 124, '', 'ACNE CONTROL DAILY SCRUB', '', 'ACNECONTROLDAILYSCRUB', 'ACNE CONTROL DAILY SCRUB', 5, 0, '2020-05-29 15:50:43', 0);
