(69, 'NU-5360', 1, 48, 27, 'NEUTROGENA Oil-Free Acne Wash Pink Grapefruit Foaming Scrub', '<p>Our acne face scrub powerfully clears blemishes and blackheads with maximum strength Salicylic Acid acne-fighting medicine plus an uplifting blast of grapefruit.</p>\r\n<p>With naturally derived grapefruit extract plus vitamin C, this oil-free scrub features gentle exfoliators that smooth away roughness without over-drying or irritating acne-prone skin.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', '', '', '3000.00', '0.00', 6, 320, '', '', '', '', '', 4, 0, '2020-05-29 15:58:44', 0),
