(71, 'LO-3986', 1, 45, 23, 'LOREAL paris NEW IDEAL CLEAN', '<h3>Gently Removes Makeup. Buffs Away Impurities. Minimizes Pores.</h3>\r\n<p>It’s never too early to start taking care of your skin. Oil free Ideal Clean Foaming Gel Cleanser gently removes makeup and buffs away impurities, leaving skin refreshed and radiant. The gel makes removing makeup quick and easy, deeply purifying while helping to minimize pores. It works for all skin types and won’t leave any tightness or residue.</p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '0.00', '0.00', 12, 1, '', '', '', '', '', 2, 0, '2020-05-29 16:08:07', 0),
