(123, '073930032502', 1, 171, 14, 'GiGi Strip Free Honee Complete Hair Waxing at Home Hair Removal Kit', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; color: #111111; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">COMPLETE AT HOME HAIR REMOVAL KIT: The GiGi Strip Free Honee Microwave Kit is a complete system for gentle, efficient removal of unwanted hair. This kit comes complete with an 8oz Strip Free Honee Microwave Formula, Pre Hon, 2oz, Wax Off 2oz, Post Wax Cooling Gel 2oz, Slow Grow 2oz, Small Accu Edge Applicators (5 pcs and Large Accu Edge Applicators (5 pcs)</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">IDEAL FOR FACE AND BODY: This GiGi Strip Free at Home Waxing Kit can be used to remove unwanted hair in the face, including upper lip and eyebrows, and the body including back, arms, legs, underarms and chest.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">EFFICIENTLY FORMULATED: This home waxing kit contains honey extract, an antioxidant-rich ingredient that moisturizes and soothes for soft glowing skin. It contains Aloe Vera and Allantoin, to help replenish lost moisture and protect the skin. It also contains Papaya enzymes was added to help slow down the regrowth of hair.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">EASY TO USE: No need for wax warmer. Remove the cap and the plastic disc, place jar in the center of a mi