(180, '1106009', 22, 41, 50, 'JOVEES STRAWBERRY FACE WASH ', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Perfect for dry and combination skin, this gentle and moisturising face wash replenishes moisture with the goodness of strawberry extracts, jojoba, and Vitamin E. The fruity fragrance rejuvenates your mood while the face wash formula rejuvenates your skin. The deep moisture also prevents early signs of ageing.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;\">HOW TO USE:</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\">Moisten your face with a splash of water.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\">Squeeze out a small coin-sized amount of the product on your palm.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\">Rub your hands together and massage gently on your face and neck.</span><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\">Rinse thoroughly and pat dry. Follow it up with a toner and a moisturiser. Use twice a day for the best results.</span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;\">KEY INGREDIENTS:</span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\">The antioxidants and Vitamin C present in strawberries nourish the skin by reducing dullness, redness, and early signs of ageing.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\">Jojoba reduces the redness caused by dry skin and keeps skin calm and comfortable.</span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: center; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold; text-transform: uppercase;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400; text-transform: none;\">Vitamin E returns lost moisture to your skin and prevents further dryness and itchiness.</span></span></span></span></p>', NULL, NULL, NULL, '730.00', '0.00', 3, 120, '8906007670142', 'FACEWASH', '', 'FACEWASH', 'FACEWASH', 3, 0, '2020-08-08 16:13:18', 0),
