(189, '1106019', 22, 48, 50, 'JOVEES DE-TAN FACE SCRUB-100G', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Sun exposure can leave your skin feeling not just tanned, but dehydrated and dull too. Wash off that tan and dullness with this blend of aloe vera, green tea leaves, and sweet cherry fruit. Apart from restoring your complexion, it also soothes the redness and inflammation of burnt skin and prevents dark spots.</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"note \" style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; display: inline-block; padding-right: 15px;\"><strong>PARABEN FREE</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"note \" style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; display: inline-block; padding-right: 15px;\"><strong>ALCOHOL FREE</strong></div>\r\n<div class=\"note \" style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; display: inline-block; padding-right: 15px;\"><strong>CRUELTY FREE</strong></div>', NULL, 'ALOE VERA\r\nAloe Vera has a healing and soothing effect on tanned and sunburnt skin. It replenishes the skin\'s moisture and evens out its tone.\r\n\r\nGREEN TEA LEAVES\r\nThe nutrients and vitamins present in green tea leaves prevent excessive melanin formation and improve skin tone.\r\n\r\nSWEET CHERRY FRUIT\r\nCherries help in reducing dark spots and sun spots that appear due to sun damage', 'Moisten your face with a splash of water.\r\nSqueeze out a small coin-sized amount of the product on your palm.\r\nRub your hands together and massage gently on your face and neck.\r\nRinse thoroughly and pat dry. Follow it up with a toner and De-Tan Face Lotion. Use twice a day for best results.', '990.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8906007675888', 'FACE SCRUB', '', 'FACESCRUB', 'FACE SCRUB', 5, 0, '2020-08-09 14:52:19', 0);
