(295, '22VG7Q54P98X', 22, 104, 53, 'Palmers Complexion Toner', '<p><span style=\"color: #957f83; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Palmer\'s Skin Success Complexion Toner contains natural exfoliants that gently remove dulling surface impurities, revealing a brighter, more luminous and balanced complexion. Skin is left feeling refreshed and clean without any dryness or uncomfortable tightness.</span></p>', 'Brightens complexion', '<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: #957f83; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Beta Hydroxy: gently exfoliates to brighten and balance complexion</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: #957f83; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Tea Tree Oil: refreshes skin and removes impurities</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: #957f83; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Witch Hazel: keeps skin clear of pore clogging dirt, oil and pollution</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 20px; color: #957f83; font-family: Tahoma, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Vitamin E: a powerful antioxidant</p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: BogleWeb, \'Helvetica Neue\', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">Moisten a clean cotton ball or cosmetic puff and smooth over face and neck.</span></p>', '2050.00', '0.00', 6, 250, '010181080012', 'Toner ', '', '', 'Toner ', 1, 0, '2020-08-24 11:16:25', 0),
(296, '22KFS7LC25VL', 22, 155, 53, 'Palmer\'s Dry Oil Mist', '<p><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Help revitalize & soften hair with Palmer\'s Coconut Dry Oil Mist. This weightless formulation helps add moisture, increase shine and combat frizz without weighing down hair. Spritz on dry, damaged or color treated hair.</span><span style=\"color: #111111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Help revitalize & soften hair with Palmer\'s Coconut Dry Oil Mist. This weightless formulation helps add moisture, increase shine and combat frizz without weighing down hair. Spritz on dry, damaged or color treated hair.</span></p>', 'Shine Dry Oil Hair Mist ', '<p><span style=\"color: #0f1111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">lsododecane, Cyclotetrasiloxane, SD Alcohol 40-B, Cetearyl Ethylhexanoate, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Oil, Tocopheryl Acetate, Cocoyl Hydrolyzed Keratin, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Argania Spinosa Kernel Oil, Emblica Officinalis (Amla) Fruit, Persea Gratissima (Avocado) Oil, Vitis Vinifera (Grape) Seed Oil, Passiflora Edulis Seed Oil, Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil, Aleurites Moluccana Seed Oil, Dimethicone, Fragrance (Parfum), Benzyl Benzoate, Coumarin, Limonene.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: #0f1111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">On clean, towel-dried hair, spray product evenly before blow drying. On dry hair- use as often as desired to boost shine and tame frizz throughout the day.</span></p>', '2850.00', '0.00', 6, 178, '010181033124', 'Dry Oil', '', '', 'Dry Oil', 2, 0, '2020-08-24 11:39:32', 0),
(297, '22XJ3UCAHGBD', 22, 155, 53, 'Palmer\'s Olive Oil Formula Weightless Shine Dry Oil Mist', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small;\">This weightless oil imparts a sheer veil of moisture to the hair, creating a protective layer with a glossy sheen. The Amla, Argan and Grape Seed Oil blend protects hair from styling tools and tames frizz. Instantly restores moisture to dry hair with Extra Virgin Olive Oil and Vitamin E. No Sulfates. No Parabens. No Phthalates. No Mineral Oil. No Gluten. No Dyes. Product directions: Spray lightly on dry hair after styling, concentrating on ends and damaged or dry-looking areas. Can be used as often as desired, or on wet hair prior to drying. Safety warnings: For external use only. Avoid contact with eyes. Keep out of reach of children. Caution: Flammable. Avoid fire, flame and heat during application until hair is fully dry. Key Ingredients: Extra Virgin Olive Oil: contains naturally occuring vitamins and minerals which act as antioxidants protecting hair and skin from damaging free radicals Amla Oil: strengthens and conditions the hair follicle with a blend of essential fatty acids, vitamin C, protein and minerals Argan Oil: produced from the kernels of the Moroccan Argan tree, this oil imparts unsurpassed shine and life to dull, lifeless hair Grape Seed Oil: contains a high amount of linolic acid which acts as a sealant, protecting hair from moisture loss Jamaican Black Castor Oil: has a strong lipid content which helps relieve dry, itchy scalp while protecting hair from styling damage</span></p>', 'Dry Oil Mist', '<div class=\"a-section content\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 22px; margin-top: 6.5px; margin-left: 25px; color: #0f1111; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: -4px 0px 14px;\">Isododecane, Cyclotetra- siloxane, Alcohol Denat., Cetearyl Ethylhexanoa