(306, '1106036', 22, 106, 50, 'JOVEES THERMOHERB FACE LIFTING-205G', '<p><span style=\"color: #666666; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Jovees Face Lift Thermoherb Mask is developed based on the ancient thermal mask, though, improved and perfected by the substitution of herbal extracts. A complete treatment in itself, this mask deep cleanses pores, restores its glow and nourishes the skin and tightens its tissues. A sophisticated technique to rejuvenate skin, this mask has been proven to give great results. The heat being generated by this mask increases the blood circulation. As the mask cools down, it hardens, tightening the pores and tissues, sculpting the jaw line, improving muscle tones and elasticity, while minimising wrinkles. It is a rejuvenating treatment almost like an instant mini face-lift. This mask acts like a total salon treatment.</span></p>', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #666666; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Multani Mitti, Ashwagandha, Liquorice, Henna.</span></p>', '<p>Clean face and massage it with Wheat Germ Face Massage Cream. After massaging for 12 minutes, apply a quarter inch thick layer of Wheat Germ Face Massage Cream again.</p>\r\n<p>Apply thermoherb (make a thick paste and quickly apply before it starts to harden) mask. Leave on for 30 minutes.</p>\r\n<p>Remove Mask gently and slowly. Wipe off excess cream. Wash face with plain water. Apply a light moisturiser.</p>', '1170.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8906007671149', 'FACE MASK', '', 'FACEMASK', 'FACE MASK', 6, 0, '2020-08-25 11:45:43', 0),
(307, '1106034', 22, 106, 50, 'JOVEES INSTA FAIR LIQUORICE GLOW PACK-400G', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Imagine that you’re spending hours and days trying to make a day extra special, but the process leaves you and your skin, tired, dull, and exhausted. Add that life back to your skin with this pack that reduces excessive melanin production, improves skin texture, and adds glow, giving you brighter and more radiant skin.</span></p>', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #636363; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">Bearberry extract, Liquorice extract, Arbutin extract, Multani Mitti and Calamine.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">Cleanse your face with a face wash and pat dry.</span><br style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; text-align: center; background-color: #ffe9c3;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">Squeeze out a walnut-sized amount of the face pack on your palm or in a container.</span><br style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; text-align: center; background-color: #ffe9c3;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">Apply a thick layer on your face and neck and leave it on for 20 minutes.</span><br style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; text-align: center; background-color: #ffe9c3;\" /><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif; text-align: center;\">Rinse thoroughly with plain water. Pat dry and follow it up with the Saffron and Bearberry Fairness Cream.</span></p>', '3070.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8906007671101', 'FACE PACK', '', 'FACEPACK', 'FACE PACK', 2, 0, '2020-08-25 11:55:37', 0),
