(349, '1105190', 22, 98, 21, 'KEUNE  STYLE BRILLIANT GLOSS SPRAY - 200ML', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W01 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">Spray on the shine Talk about shine… we’ve taken gloss to the max with N°110 Brilliant Gloss Spray, with level 10 shine. For instant shine after styling, just mist over dry hair. This fine oil-free formula is the feather-light finishing touch to any hairstyle, with only the slightest amount of factor 1 hold. For that special glow that comes from healthy, happy hair</span></p>', 'Adds super shine\r\nUV Filter\r\nSmooths frizz\r\n\r\n', '', '', '1900.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281039631', 'HAIR SPRAY', '', 'HAIRSPRAY,SPRAY,GLOSSSPRAY,BRILLIANTGLOSSSPRAY,KEUNE', 'HAIR SPRAY,BRILLIANT GLOSS SPRAY', 5, 0, '2020-09-05 18:58:00', 0),
(350, '1105284', 22, 98, 21, 'KEUNE BLEND GLOSS SPRAY-150ML', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2.2rem; margin: 0px 0px 3rem; -webkit-box-direction: initial; -webkit-box-orient: initial; flex-direction: row; font-family: \'Futura PT W01 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow: hidden; color: #3c3c3b; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">Love that power. With all those original styles or that explosive volume you love creating, you need a darned good hairspray. Blend Fixing Spray by Keune does its job all day long – and won’t let you down during wild nights on the town.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2.2rem; margin: 0px 0px 3rem; -webkit-box-direction: initial; -webkit-box-orient: initial; flex-direction: row; font-family: \'Futura PT W01 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow: hidden; color: #3c3c3b; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">You can use Blend Fixing Spray as a working or a fixing hairspray – either way, you’re going to get powerful hold unlike any other. Just make sure to do all your teasing, brushing and styling super fast, before the spray dries. Because once it’s dry, it’s set to level 10 hold – the highest holding power Keune makes. Smells nice, too!</p>', 'Lovely glossy hair\r\nConditions and nourishes\r\nNot greasy\r\n\r\nMaximum hold without that dreaded helmet-head sensation. Don’t worry about using it on colored hair – we made it safe. And when its time for bed, it’s easy to muss and brush out.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nAny hair length / type.\r\n\r\nHold factor : LEVEL 1\r\nShine factor: LEVEL 10\r\n', '', '', '2925.00', '0.00', 2, 1, '8718734856474', 'HAIR SPRAY', '', 'HAIRSPRAY,GLOSSSPRAY,BLENDSPRAY,KEUNEPRODUCTS,BLEND', '', 4, 1, '2020-09-06 12:05:30', 0),
(351, '1105286', 22, 98, 21, 'KEUNE BLEND SEA SALT SPRAY AU SEL MARIN-150ML', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2.2rem; margin: 0px 0px 3rem; -webkit-box-direction: initial; -webkit-box-orient: initial; flex-direction: row; font-family: \'Futura PT W01 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow: hidden; color: #3c3c3b; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">The best thing about the beach is… the beach. Second on our list is that great textured, messy hair you get to take home with you. With our Blend Sea Salt Spray, you get all that weightless body and volume with just a few spritzes of the bottle.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 16px; line-height: 2.2rem; margin: 0px 0px 3rem; -webkit-box-direction: initial; -webkit-box-orient: initial; flex-direction: row; font-family: \'Futura PT W01 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; overflow: hidden; color: #3c3c3b; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">But it’s not just about the sea salt. To condition and nourish hair, we also blended in our multi-vitamin complex. Feel free to mix it with any of the 14 Blend products, to create that perfectly imperfect look that looks so relaxed. Just like you feel after a day at the beach.</p>', 'Volume\r\nbody and texture\r\nMatte finish\r\n\r\nConditions and nourishes\r\nInstant beachy texture, body and volume. Creates a rough and messy effect without drying or tangling hair. For normal to fine hair, and all lengths.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nNormal to fine hair. Any hairlength.\r\n\r\nHold factor : LEVEL 5\r\nShine factor : LEVEL 1\r\n', '', '', '3150.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8718734856344', 'HAIR SPRAY', '', 'HAIRSPRAY,SPRAY,SEASALTSPRAY,KEUNEPRODUCTS,SELMARIN', '', 9, 0, '2020-09-06 12:19:24', 0),
(352, 'MT', 23, 143, 19, 'Jordana Modern Matte Lipstick', '', 'You\'re sure to go mad for this matte! The days of dry lips are over—Modern Matte Lipstick stays vibrant and soft-to-the-touch, all day long.\r\nNo feathering or cracking, just perfectly smooth, soft lips and worry-free wear!', '', '', '890.00', '0.00', 6, 4, '', 'Jordana Modern Matte Lipstick', '', 'MatteLipstick', 'Modern Matte Lipstick', 20, 0, '2020-09-09 15:26:37', 0),
(353, 'MLC', 23, 144, 19, 'JORDANA Sweet Cream Matte Liquid Lip Color', '<p>Infused with a drop of vitamin A-- Sweet Cream Matte Liquid Lip Color keeps lips comfortable and never dry. Each tempting shade stays fresh on your lips for up to 16 hours. You just got one step closer to yum!</p>', 'Give your lips some sugar, sweetie! Sweet Cream Matte Liquid Lip Color starts off as a liquid and melts into a velvety matte finish. Indulge in a light, creamy-whipped feel and dessert-rich shades like Cherry Cobbler and Red Velvet Cake.', '<p>Isododecane, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Cyclopentasiloxane, Dimethicone, Kaolin, Flavor (Aroma), Hydrogenated Polyisobutene, Synthetic Beeswax, Silica Dimethyl Silylate, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Phenoxyethanol, Caprylyl Glycol, Hexylene Glycol, Tocopheryl Acetate.</p>\r\n<p>+/- May Contain: Red 30 Lake (CI 73360), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Red 6 Lake (CI 15859), Red 7 Lake (CI 15850), Yellow 5 Lake (CI 19140), Red 28 (CI 45410).</p>', '<p>Apply Sweet Cream Matte Liquid Lip Color starting in the center of your upper lip and work toward the outer edge. The same technique applies for your bottom lip.</p>', '1990.00', '0.00', 6, 5, '', 'Sweet Cream Matte Liquid Lip Color', '', 'LiquidLipColor', 'Sweet Cream Matte Liquid Lip Color', 27, 1, '2020-09-09 15:56:31', 0),
(354, 'CCF', 23, 8, 19, 'Jordana Complete Cover 2-In-1 Concealer & Foundation', '<p>Complete Cover 2-in-1 Concealer & Foundation = the ultimate in double-duty beauty!</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Max full coverage</li>\r\n<li>Oil-free formula</li>\r\n<li>Evens out skin tone</li>\r\n<li>Blurs the look of flaws</li>\r\n<li>Suitable for all skin types</li>\r\n<li>Made in USA</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Meet your secret weapon for making dark circles and spots look like they’ve vanished! Complete Cover 2-in-1 Concealer & Foundation evens out skin tone when applied as an all-over foundation, and also works as a full coverage concealer—just dab onto trouble spots for a quick fix.', '<p>Water (Aqua), Cyclopentasiloxane, Isononyl Isononanoate, Cetyl PEG/PPG-10/1 Dimethicone, Butylene Glycol, Polyisobutene, C18-21 Alkane, Glycerin, Bis-PEG/PPG-14/14 Dimethicone, Bis-Vinyl Dimethicone/Dimethicone Copolymer, VP/Eicosene Copolymer, Ozokerite, Polymethylsilsesquioxane, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Sodium Chloride, Phenoxyethanol, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Glycereth-18 Ethylhexanoate, Potassium Sorbate, Silica, Caprylyl Glycol, 1,2-Hexanediol, Isododecane, Xanthan Gum, Propylene Carbonate, Glycereth-18, Triethoxycaprylylsilane, Aluminum Dimyristate, Allantoin, Disodium Stearoyl Glutamate, C30-45 Alkyl Cetearyl Dimethicone Crosspolymer, +/- May Contain: Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499).</p>', '<p>As a Foundation</p>\r\n<p>Choose a shade that is closest to your natural skin tone. With fingertips, a makeup sponge or a foundation brush, apply Complete Cover 2-in-1 Concealer & Foundation to the center of your face—chin, forehead and the tip of your nose—moving outward as you go.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>As a Concealer</p>\r\n<p>Choose a shade that is closest to your natural skin tone. Dab Complete Cover 2-in-1 Concealer & Foundation onto trouble areas using your fingertips.</p>', '1990.00', '0.00', 6, 15, '', 'Complete Cover 2-In-1 Concealer & Foundation', '', 'ConcealerFoundation', 'Complete Cover 2-In-1 Concealer & Foundation', 15, 0, '2020-09-09 16:16:46', 0),
(355, 'LS', 23, 143, 19, 'Jordana Lipstick', '<p>Luscious red lips or a hot pink pout—who can resist? Be bold with Lipstick! It looks good on you! Plus kisses are WAY better in color!</p>\r\n<p>This lipstick glides on rich and creamy with a light-as-air feel.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Full coverage color</p>\r\n<p>Pearl, cream and frosted finishes</p>\r\n<p>Non-drying, silky feel</p>\r\n<p>Glides on smooth—no skipping</p>', 'Luscious red lips or a hot pink pout—who can resist? Be bold with Lipstick! It looks good on you! Plus kisses are WAY better in color!\r\n\r\nThis lipstick glides on rich and creamy with a light-as-air feel.', '<p>Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Propylene Glycol Myristyl Ether Acetate, Isostearyl Palmitate, Euphorbia Cerifera (Candelilla) Wax (Candelilla Cera), Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Synthetic Beeswax, Lanolin, Fragrance (Parfum), Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax (Cera Carnauba), Ozokerite, Beeswax (Cera Alba), Cetyl Alcohol, VP/Hexadecene Copolymer, Tocopheryl Acetate, Propylparaben, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Tocopherol, Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil.</p>\r\n<p>+/- May Contain: Mica, Zinc Oxide, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Red 6 (CI 15850), Red 7 (CI 15850), Red 22 (CI 45380), Red 27 (CI 45410), Red 28 (CI 45410), Yellow 5 (CI 19140), Yellow 6 (CI 15985), Blue 1 (CI 42090), Carmine (CI 75470), Red 33 (CI 17200), Red 36 (CI 12085), Red 21 (CI 45380).</p>', '<p>Apply Lipstick starting in the center of your upper lip and work toward the outer edge. The same technique applies for your bottom lip.</p>', '650.00', '0.00', 6, 4, '', 'Lipstick', '', 'Lipstick', 'JORDANALipstick', 3, 0, '2020-09-10 14:14:12', 0),
(356, 'MG', 23, 143, 19, 'Jordana Matte Lipstick', '<p>Super-saturated color</p>\r\n<p>Opaque matte finish</p>\r\n<p>Infused with antioxidants for moisture</p>\r\n<p>Easy to apply</p>\r\n<p>Stays put all day</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>', 'Date night and nothing to wear? Don\'t worry! Velvety Matte Lipstick ensures that no one will be looking at just your outfit.\r\nWith the perfect blast of show stopping color and a non-drying matte finish—your lips will speak for you!', '<p>Ricinus Communis (Castor) Seed Oil, Propylene Glycol Myristyl Ether Acetate, Cetyl Acetate Talc, Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Ozokerite, Euphorbia Cerifera Cera (Candellia Wax), Copernicia Cerifera Cera (Carnauba Wax), Synthetic Beeswax, Fragrance (Parfum), VP/Hexadecene, Copolymer, Lanolin, Acetylated Lanolin Alcohol, Aluminum Starch Octenylsuccinate, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Tocopheryl Acetate, Propylparaben, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil Tocopherol, Alumina, Mica.</p>\r\n<p>+/- May Contain: Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Carmine (CI 75470), Bismuth Chloride Oxide (CI 77163), Manganese Violet (CI 77742), Blue 1 Lake (CI 42090), Yellow 5 Lake (CI 19140), Yellow 6 Lake (CI 15985), Red 6 Lake (CI 15850), Red 7 Lake (CI 15850), Red 28 Lake (CI 45410), Red 22 Lake (CI 45380).</p>', '<p>Apply Matte Lipstick starting in the center of your upper lip and work toward the outer edge. The same technique applies for your bottom lip.</p>', '650.00', '0.00', 6, 4, '', 'JORDANA Matte Lipstick', '', 'MatteLipstick', 'Matte Lipstick', 53, 0, '2020-09-10 17:31:37', 0),
(359, '011509049315', 24, 102, 20, 'Just for men darkest brown h-50', '<p>The ammonia-free formula lasts up to 6 weeks, until the gray grows out. Check out our How-To to see how easy it is!</p>', 'Just For Men targets only the gray hair. Replaces it with subtle tones that match your own natural color in 5 easy minutes. ', '<p>water,ethoxydiglycol,c11-15 pareth-3,canola oil fatty acids,ethanolamine,p-phenylenediamine,resorcinol,oleyl alcohol,n,n-bis(2-hydroxyethy)-p-phenylenediamine sulfate,m-aminophenol,4-choloresocinol,fragrance,1-naphthol,sodium sulfate.</p>', '', '2500.00', '0.00', 6, 50, '011509049315', 'Just for men darkest brown h-50', '', 'haircolour', 'Just for men darkest brown h-50', 6, 0, '2020-09-12 12:57:22', 0),
