(382, '1105418', 22, 92, 21, 'KEUNE REFRESH STYLE DRY SHAMPOO 200ml', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">Waiting between washes is a good thing, but hair can get oily and limp by day 2 or 3. Not to mention 4. Even 1st day hair feels better with N°11 Dry Shampoo. Because it immediately refreshes hair by absorbing oils and other impurities. Just spray on hair’s roots for instantly gratifying freshness and extra fullness – without telltale white residue.</span></p>', 'Absorbs oils and impurities, to instantly refresh hair between washes while adding fullness. For all hair types, especially those prone to oiliness.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nAll hair types prone to oiliness.\r\n\r\n#Hold factor: LEVEL 1\r\n#Shine factor: LEVEL 1 ', '', '', '2250.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281039693', 'DRY SHAMPOO', '', 'DRYSHAMPOO,KEUNESTYLESHAMPOO,KEUNEPRODUCTS', '', 7, 0, '2020-09-19 12:23:43', 0),
(383, '1105419', 22, 91, 21, 'KEUNE REFRESH STYLE DRY CONDITIONER-200ml', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">We want shine, and we want it now. All it takes is a spray of N°15 Dry Conditioner. This instant conditioner has some of the benefits of our dry shampoo – like absorbing oils and leaving no white residue. But it also detangles hair and adds nice, natural shine. For soft, totally touchable hair without a drop of water.</span></p>', 'Feather-light dry conditioning spray that leaves hair soft and detangled, for all types of hair.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nAll hair types\r\n\r\nHold factor: LEVEL 1\r\nShine factor: LEVEL 5\r\n\r\n', '', '', '2400.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281039679', 'DRY CONDITIONER', '', 'STYLECONDITIONER,DRYCONDITIONER,KEUNEPRODUCTS', 'DRY CONDITIONER', 6, 0, '2020-09-19 13:02:24', 0),
(384, '1105417', 22, 98, 21, 'KEUNE REFRESH STYLE DRY TEXTURIZER 200ml', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">Farewell flat hair. All you need is a few sprays of N°61 Dry Texturizer for a nice bit of extra grip and texture. This is flexible hold, that feels and looks natural, thanks to our Dry Cleansing Complex – which absorbs oils and adds texture without leaving a white residue behind. So it’s just texture and you (and the rest is nobody’s business).</span></p>', 'Invisible, dry texturizing spray for all types of hair that absorbs oils and adds volume and texture, with medium hold.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nAll hair types\r\n\r\nHold factor: LEVEL 6\r\nShine factor: LEVEL 1\r\n\r\n', '', '', '2430.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281039723', 'SPRAY', '', 'HAIRSPRAY,SPRAY,DRYSPRAY,TEXTURIZERSPRAY,KEUNEPRODUCTS', '', 5, 1, '2020-09-19 13:38:33', 0),
(385, '1105299', 22, 98, 21, 'KEUNE HEAT PROTECT STYLE INSTANT BLOWOUT-200ml', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">Spend more time doing what you love best – styling beautiful hair – with N°37 Instant Blowout. Created for fine to normal hair, it speeds up blow-drying prep work while protecting hair from heat up to 230°C (450°F). And did we mention the lightweight body and wonderful shine? N°37 Instant Blowout can also be layered with other Keune Style products.</span></p>', 'Heat-protecting spray for fine to normal hair that speeds up blow drying prep, and adds lightweight volume and factor 7 shine.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nFine to normal hair.\r\n\r\nHold factor: LEVEL 3\r\nShine facto: LEVEL 7', '', '', '2325.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281040071', 'HAIR SPRAY', '', 'HAIRSPRAY,SPRAY,BLOWOUTSPRAY,HEATPROTECTSPRAY,KEUNE,STYLESPRAY', '', 4, 0, '2020-09-19 13:50:35', 0),
(386, '1105409', 22, 98, 21, 'KEUNE VOLUME STYLE STRONG MOUSSE-200ml', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">For volume that makes a real statement, go for N°74 Strong Mousse. With factor 7 hold, it’s got the power to add incredible volume and fullness, with a nice touch of shine. Strong styling polymers keeps hair in style – while conditioners like panthenol condition and strengthen hair.</span></p>', 'Prep hair with volume that lasts with N°74 Strong Mousse, to condition hair while creating lasting volume.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nNormal to thick hair.\r\n\r\nHold factor: LEVEL 7\r\nShine factor: LEVEL 4\r\n', '', '', '1575.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281040026', 'HAIR MOUSSE', '', 'HAIRMOUSSE,MOUSSE,STYLEMOUSSE,VOLUMESTRONGMOUSSE,KEUNEPRODUCT', '', 12, 0, '2020-09-19 15:19:05', 0),
