(393, 'NL', 23, 145, 19, 'Jordana Classic Color Lipliner', '<p>Classic Color Lipliner keeps lipstick from feathering and helps to make your look last! You can also opt to wear it on its own for a true matte look.</p>\r\n<p>Lines and accentuates</p>\r\n<p>Soft matte finish</p>\r\n<p>Keeps lipstick from feathering</p>\r\n<p>Extends the wear of lipstick</p>\r\n<p>Can be worn on its own</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', 'Are you a Classic Red kind of girl? Maybe Spiced Rum complements your style best. You\'ve got options—and options are a girl\'s best friend!\r\n\r\nNo matter what color you choose, this soft matte lipliner is sure to accentuate and define the curves of your lips beautifully.\r\n\r\n', '<p>Coco-Caprylate/Caprate, Euphorbia Cerifera Cera (Candellia Wax), Hydrogenated Coco-Glycerides, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Sucrose Acetate Isobutyrate, Copernicia Cerifera Cera (Carnauba Wax), Caprylic/Capric Triglycerides, Zinc Stearate.</p>\r\n<p>+/- May Contain: Mica, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77499, CI 77492, CI 77491), Red 7 (CI 15850), Yellow 6 (CI 15985), Red 28 (CI 45410), Red 30 (CI 73360), Blue 1 (CI 42090), Bismuth Oxychloride (CI 77163).</p>', '<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Trace the curves of your natural lip line with Classic Color Lipliner starting at the outer corner, and move toward the center. Connect the lines as you go.</p>', '590.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', 'Classic Color Lipliner', '', 'Lipliner', 'Classic Color Lipliner', 2, 0, '2020-09-26 10:26:22', 0),
(394, 'LES', 23, 192, 19, 'Jordana Made to Last Liquid Eyeshadow', '<p> </p>\r\n<p>Blendable liquid eyeshadow</p>\r\n<p>Up to 16HR wear</p>\r\n<p>Creamy, non-tacky texture</p>\r\n<p>Crease-proof and water-resistant</p>\r\n<p>Built-in applicator</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>', 'Meet our newest nudes! Made to Last Liquid Eyeshadow is a smooth liquid shadow that melts onto lids and just won\'t quit!\r\n\r\nHighly saturated with metallic color—from neutral pinks to bronzed metals—and decorated with light-reflecting pearls, the 16-hour wear shadow is also crease-proof and water-resistant.\r\n\r\n', '<p>Water (Aqua), Triethylhexanoin, Vinyl Dimethicone/Methicone Silsesquioxane Crosspolymer, Acrylates Copolymer, Silica, Glycerin, Pentylene Glycol, Alcohol Denat., Phenoxyethanol, Sodium Acrylate/Sodium Acryloyldimethyl Taurate Copolymer, Isohexadecane, Glyceryl Stearate, Sorbitan Sesquioleate, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Potassium Cetyl Phosphate, PEG-100 Stearate, Triceteareth-4 Phosphate, Glycol Stearate, Tocopheryl Acetate, PEG-2 Stearate, Polysorbate 80, Ethylhexylglycerin, Sodium Polyacrylate, Xanthan Gum, Calcium Titanium Borosilicate, Synthetic Fluorphlogopite, Sorbitan Oleate, Mica.</p>\r\n<p>+/- May Contain: Tin Oxide (CI 77861), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77491), Iron Oxides (CI 77499), Ferric Ferrocyanide (CI 77510).</p>', '<p>Sweep a pretty shade of Made to Last Liquid Eyeshadow across lid, blending up and out. </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Daytime look</p>\r\n<p>Start by sweeping Immortal Metal across entire lid. Then highlight with Not a Wink Pink along the inner-to-mid crease, and finish by adding an accent of Forever Sand in the inner corners of lids. </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Nighttime look</p>\r\n<p>Sweep Around Town Brown across your entire lid, then highlight with Dusk ‘Til Bronze along the inner-to-mid crease and accent with Uphold Gold on the inner corners of lids.</p>', '995.00', '0.00', 6, 4, '', 'Made to Last Liquid Eyeshadow', '', 'LiquidEyeshadow', 'Made to Last Liquid Eyeshadow', 3, 0, '2020-09-26 15:52:57', 0),
(395, 'LEP', 23, 136, 19, 'Jordana  Made to Last Eyeshadow Primer', '<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Intensifies any eyeshadow color</p>\r\n<p>Prevents creasing and fading</p>\r\n<p>Easy blending for a pro look</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>\r\n<p> </p>', 'Don\'t let that color get lost!\r\n\r\nMake shadows more vibrant and less likely to crease or fade by applying a quick dab of the light and creamy Made to Last Eyeshadow Primer to your lids!\r\n\r\nDay to night—you look fabulous and you know it!', '<p>Isododecane, Talc, Mica, Cyclopentasiloxane, Disteardimonium Hectorite, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Trihydroxystearin, Polyethylene, Triethylhexanoin, Sorbitan Sesquioleate, VP/Eicosene Copolymer, Dimethicone, Dipalmitoyl Hydroxyproline, Phenoxyethanol, PEG-40 Stearate, Synthetic Beeswax, Propylene Carbonate, Ethylhexylglycerin, Water (Aqua), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Bismuth Oxychloride (CI 77163), Iron Oxide (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499).</p>', '<p> </p>\r\n<p>Apply Made to Last Eyeshadow Primer to clean, dry lids and blend well. Allow to set for 30 seconds. Works on all skin tones. </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Tip: Get glam with non-stop color! Sweep a pretty shade of Eye Glam Cream Eyeshadow on top!</p>', '1150.00', '0.00', 6, 8, '', 'Made to Last Eyeshadow Primer', '', 'EyeshadowPrimer', 'Made to Last Eyeshadow Primer', 0, 0, '2020-09-26 16:12:31', 0),
(396, 'BD', 23, 142, 19, 'Jordana Brow Powder Duo', '<p> </p>\r\n<p>Full pigment</p>\r\n<p>Matte finish</p>\r\n<p>Dual-ended slanted brush with sponge applicator</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>', 'Get the best brows in the business! Brow Powder Duo makes getting defined, naturally fuller-looking brows easy! Mix and match two shades of powder and apply to brows, blending as you go. Fill in sparse brow areas and shape arches with the angled side of the dual-ended brush. The powders are so versatile that you can also use them as an eyeshadow duo. Just apply the light and dark shades directly to the lid with the sponge applicator side. It\'s the best of both worlds!\r\n\r\n', '<p>Talc, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Zinc Stearate, Dimethicone, Lauroyl Lysine, Trimethylsiloxysilicate, Sodium Dehydroacetate, Methylparaben, Propylparaben, Butylparaben, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Tocopherol, Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil, Iron Oxides (CI 77499), Bismuth Oxychloride (CI 77163). +/-May Contain: Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492), Ultramarines (CI 77007), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Manganese Violet (CI 77742).</p>', '<p>How to apply: Apply and blend brow powder colors to fill and shape perfect looking brows.</p>', '790.00', '0.00', 6, 5, '', 'Brow Powder Duo', '', 'BrowPowder', 'Brow Powder Duo', 4, 0, '2020-09-26 16:16:45', 0),
(397, '23IM0IMHZHP3', 23, 142, 19, 'Jordana Fabubrow Eyebrow Pencil', '<p>Colors, fills, defines</p>\r\n<p>Creamy, lightweight feel</p>\r\n<p>Sharpens to a fine point</p>\r\n<p>Cap with grooming brush</p>\r\n<p>Made in Germany</p>', 'Never let anyone with bad brows tell you how to live your life. Instead, show them how to magically create their own perfect brows in seconds!\r\nThe Fabubrow Eyebrow Pencil has an extra fine point that makes it easy to draw natural-looking brow hairs with just a few quick strokes.\r\nThen, use the brush on the opposite end of the pencil to soften the look. Bad brow problem, solved!\r\n', '<p> </p>\r\n<p>Hydrogenated Palm Kernel Glycerides, Cera Microcristallina (Microcrystalline Wax), Mica, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides, Myristyl Myristate, Hydrogenated Coco-Glycerides, Copernica Cerifera Cera (Carnauba Wax), Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Rhus Succedanea Cera (Fruit Wax), Sorbitan Palmitate, Stearalkonium Hectorite, Propylene Carbonate, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-di-t-Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Tocopheryl Acetate, Tocopherol, Lecithin, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Glyceryl Stearate, Glyceryl Oleate, Citric Acid.</p>\r\n<p>+/- May Contain: Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499).</p>', '<p>First, comb untamed brow hairs with the built-in brush. Then, use quick strokes to draw tiny lines, mimicking brow hairs.</p>', '790.00', '0.00', 6, 2, '', 'Fabubrow Eyebrow Pencil', '', 'EyebrowPencil', 'Fabubrow Eyebrow Pencil', 2, 0, '2020-09-26 17:21:00', 0),
(398, 'QMP', 23, 142, 19, 'Jordana Quickbrow Micro Eyebrow Pencil', '<p>Define arches and fill in sparse areas with one end, and groom brows with the built-in brush on the other.</p>', 'You\'ve met your official brow BFF! Just a few strokes of QuickBrow Micro Pencil\'s super fine retractable tip mimic your own brow hairs so perfectly, the result is natural-looking yet flawless brows that stay smear-free.\r\n', '<p>Dicalcium Phosphate, Polyethylene, Isododecane, Hydrogenated Styrene/Methylstyrene/Indene Synthetic Copolymer, Synthetic Japanese Wax, Octyldocecanol, Vp/Hexadecene Copolymer, Mica (Ci 77019), Disteardimonium Hectorite, Polyhydroxystearic Acid, Propylene Carbonate, Lecithin, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-Di-T –Butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Citric Acid.</p>\r\n<p>+/- May Contain: Iron Oxides (Ci 77491, Ci 77492, Ci 77499), Titanium Dioxide (Ci 77891).</p>', '<p>Using small strokes, start in the middle of the brow and work toward the front, filling in sparse areas as you go and working your way to the brow end.</p>\r\n<p>Use the brush to groom hairs in an upward motion.</p>', '990.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', 'Quickbrow Micro Eyebrow Pencil', '', 'MicroEyebrowPencil', 'Quickbrow Micro Eyebrow Pencil', 3, 0, '2020-09-26 18:12:43', 0),
(399, '23RAK8K4LIXC', 23, 139, 19, 'Jordana Best Liner For Brow and Eye - 7 Eyeliner Pencil', '<p>Rich color intensity</p>\r\n<p>Lines, defines, accentuates</p>\r\n<p>Smooth and comfortable wear</p>\r\n<p>Made in Mexico</p>\r\n<p> </p>', 'Bigger is better and that’s just what you need to get those precise lines—and get them right with just one stroke! 7” Eyeliner Pencil is longer than most liners, making it easy to maneuver around the natural shape of your eye for a line that is too perfect for words!\r\n\r\n', '<p>Hydrogenated Palm Kernel Glycerides, Hydrogenated Palm Glycerides, Copernica Cerifera Cera (Carnauba Wax), Rhus Succedanea Fruit Cera (Fruit Wax), Hydrogenated Cottonseed Oil, Canola Oil, Hydrogenated Vegetable Oil, Polymethyl Methacrylate, Hydrogenated Polyisobutene, Polybutene, Silica, Mica Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Methylparaben, Propylparaben, Butylparaben, Citric Acid. +/- MAY CONTAIN: Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77491), Iron Oxide (CI 77492), Iron Oxide (CI 77499), Aluminum Powder (CI 77000), Ferric Ferrocyanide (CI 77510), Chromium Hydroxide Green (CI 77289), Blue 1 (CI 42090), Ultramarines (CI 77007), Ferric Ammonium Ferrocyanide, Carmine (CI 75470), Bismuth Oxychloride (CI 77163).</p>', '<p>Draw a line with 7” Eyeliner Pencil starting at the inner corner of lid and move toward the outer corner. Create a classic cat eye by extending the line slightly past your outer lid with an upward flick!</p>', '690.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', 'Best Liner For Brow & Eye - 7', '', 'BestEyelinerPencil', 'Best Liner For Brow & Eye - 7', 4, 0, '2020-09-26 19:04:12', 0),
