(401, 'ME', 23, 193, 19, 'Jordana 12 Hour Made To Last Liquid Eyeliner Pencil', '<p>Intense color payoff</p>\r\n<p>Lines, defines, accentuates</p>\r\n<p>Long-lasting—up to 12 HR wear</p>\r\n<p>Water-resistant and transfer-resistant</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>\r\n<p> </p>', 'Now date night can go all night! 12 HR Made to Last Liquid Eyeliner Pencil is water-resistant and transfer-resistant, which means your look will last! Perfect for beauty beginners—the smooth liquid-like tip creates thin to thick lines with ease! Sharpen with Slimline Sharpener.\r\n\r\n', '<p>Isododecane, Synthetic Wax, Cyclopentasiloxane, PEG/PPG-19/19 Dimethicone, Hydrogenated Polydicyclopentadiene, Nylon-12, C20-40 Alcohols, Calcium Aluminum Borosilicate, Silica, Perfluorononyl Dimethicone, Polyglyceryl-4 Diisostearate/Polyhydroxystearate/Sebacate Polyethylene, Pentaerythrityl Tetra-di-t-butyl Hydroxyhydrocinnamate, Tin Oxide, Tocopherol, Mica. +/- May Contain: Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499), Ultramarines (CI 77007), Ferric Ammonium Ferrocyanide (CI 77510), Blue 1 Lake (CI 42090), Chromium Oxide Greens (CI 77288), Carmine (CI 75470), Black 2 (CI 77266), Ferric Ferrocyanide (CI 77510).</p>', '<p>How to apply: Apply a thin line of 12 Hr Made to Last Liquid Eyeliner Pencil from the inner to the outer corner of your lid along your upper and lower lash line. Keep the line thin or add another layer for a thick, bold line. </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Tip: Add a splash of color to your look with Dramatic Effects Mascara!</p>', '890.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', '12 Hour Made To Last Liquid Eyeliner Pencil', '', 'LiquidEyelinerPencil', 'Eyeliner Pencil', 3, 0, '2020-09-28 14:06:44', 0),
(402, '1105428', 22, 99, 21, 'KEUNE STYLE ULTRA GEL FORTE-200ML', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Our N°88 Ultra Gel is all about the structure, shine – and amazing hold. This is gel for today’s hairstyles, and for people who love intense shine. So go wild and sculpt or set hair how you like it. N°88 Ultra Gel also offers heat protection up to 230°C (450°F) – so grab a blow dryer and have fun transforming hair with natural definition and texture.</span></p>', 'Versatile, modern gel with luminous shine and long-lasting hold for hair types, with heat protection up to 230°C (450°F).\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nAll hair types\r\n\r\nHold factor: LEVEL 8\r\nShine factor: LEVEL 8\r\n', '', '', '1490.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281040224', 'KEUNE ULTRA GEL', '', 'KEUNEGEL,ULTRAGEL,GEL,KEUNEPRODUCTS,HAIRGEL', '', 4, 0, '2020-09-29 12:52:25', 0),
(403, '23N85D1HOUEB', 23, 139, 19, 'Jordana Color Xtend Eyeliner', '<p>Full vibrant color</p>\r\n<p>Velvety smooth texture</p>\r\n<p>Long-wearing</p>\r\n<p>Waterproof and transfer-proof</p>\r\n<p>Made in Germany</p>', 'This liner has got you covered for late-night parties and all day meet-ups thanks to a super long-lasting formula and bold, black color. Easy to apply in one velvety smooth stroke, Color Xtend Eyeliner is a makeup beginner\'s best friend! Strong is the name of your new eyeliner game—trust us.', '<p>Cyclopentasiloxane, Paraffin, C11-12 Isoparaffin, Polybutene, Hydrogenated Cottonseed Oil, Simmondsia Chinensis (Jojoba) Seed Oil, Ceresin, Ozokerite, Cera Microcristallina (Microcrystalline Wax), Tocopherol, Ascorbyl Palmitate, Mica. +/- May Contain: Ferric Ferrocyanide (CI 77510), Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide (CI 77499).</p>', '<p> </p>\r\n<p>How To Apply: Draw a line starting at the inner corner of lid and move toward the outer corner. Keep the line thin and precise or smudge for a pretty smoky eye!\\</p>', '890.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', 'Color Xtend Eyeliner', '', 'Eyeliner', 'Color Xtend Eyeliner', 2, 0, '2020-09-30 15:55:41', 0),
(404, 'EE', 23, 139, 19, 'Jordana Easyliner Retractable Eye Pencil', '', 'Just like your best friend, you can always count on this smudge-, life-, and clutz-proof liner! Easyliner for Eyes comes in a variety of colors and glides on with ease—no skipping or tugging, and it\'s retractable—so no sharpening required! You\'ll want to take it with you wherever you go, just like your best friend!', '', '', '890.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', 'Easyliner Retractable Eye Pencil', '', 'RetractableEyePencil', 'Easyliner Retractable Eye Pencil', 3, 0, '2020-09-30 17:11:57', 0),
(405, 'NE', 23, 139, 19, 'Jordana Classic Color Eyeliner Pencil', '<p>Rich, stay-true color</p>\r\n<p>Lines, defines, accentuates</p>\r\n<p>Creates precise lines or soft smoky eyes</p>\r\n<p>Lightweight creamy feel</p>\r\n<p>Glides on smooth</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>', 'No matter the style—classic winged-eye, extreme cat eye, or double-lined and intense—make the Classic Color Eyeliner Pencil your go-to beauty weapon of choice!\r\nThe creamy liner glides on smooth with stay-true color, doesn\'t snag or skip and lasts all day! A classic triple threat!\r\n\r\n', '<p>Coco-Caprylate/Caprate, Euphorbia Cerifera Cera(Candellia Wax), Hydrogenated Coco-Glycerides, Cera Alba (Beeswax), Sucrose Acetate Isobutyrate, Copernicia Cerifera Cera (Carnauba Wax), Caprylic/Capric Triglycerides, Zinc Stearate, Helianthus Annuus Seed Cera (Sunflower Seed Wax),Rosmarinus Officinalis (Rosemary) Leaf Extract.</p>\r\n<p>+/- May Contain: Mica, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxide(CI 77499, CI 77492, CI 77491), Ferric Ferrocyanide (CI 77510), Ferric Ammonium Ferrocyanide (CI 77510), Blue 1 (CI 42090), Black 2 (CI 77266), Aluminum Powder(CI 77000), Manganese Violet (CI 77742), Bismuth Oxychloride (CI 77163), Carmine(CI 75470), Ultramarines (CI 77007), Chromium Oxide Greens (CI 77288).</p>', '<p>Draw a line with Classic Color Eyeliner Pencil starting at the inner corner of lid and move toward the outer corner. </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Tip: Choose a different shade of Classic Color Eyeliner Pencil to line your lower lash line!</p>', '590.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', 'Classic Color Eyeliner Pencil', '', 'ColorEyelinerPencil', 'Classic Color Eyeliner Pencil', 3, 0, '2020-09-30 19:04:45', 0),
(406, 'LL', 23, 194, 19, 'Jordana Liquid liner', '<p>Sensational color</p>\r\n<p>Lines, defines, accentuates</p>\r\n<p>Creates thin or thick lines</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>', 'Don’t just wing it! Liquid Liner can help you master any liquid-lined look! A quick flick past the outer corner of your eye brings glamour like nothing else can and adding a second flick above it creates a unique graphic eye. The fine tip of the brush makes any style effortless—one beautiful eye at a time!\r\n\r\n', '', '', '890.00', '0.00', 6, 3, '', 'JORDANA LIQUID LINER.', '', 'LIQUIDLINER', 'JORDANA LIQUID LINER.', 2, 0, '2020-10-02 11:17:43', 0),
(407, 'FB', 23, 194, 19, 'Jordana Fabuliner Liquid Eyeliner', '<p>Felt-tip liquid eyeliner</p>\r\n<p>Lines, defines, accentuates</p>\r\n<p>Creates thin or thick lines</p>\r\n<p>Glides on smooth and snag-free</p>\r\n<p>Quick drying formula</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>', 'Make looking fabulous, effortless! Fabuliner Liquid Eyeliner takes the guesswork out of perfectly liquid-lined eyes!\r\nMaster any line style—from thin feline-flicks to bold, thick lines just by adding a second swipe! One liquid liner for every kind of drama!\r\n\r\n', '<p>Water (Aqua), Propylene Glycol, Triethanolamine, Oleyl Alcohol, Magnesium Aluminum Stearate, Stearic Acid, Glyceryl Stearate, Cellulose, Hectorite, Xanthum Gum, Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer, Isopropylparaben, Butylparaben, Isobutylparaben.</p>\r\n<p>+/-May Contain: Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499).</p>', '<p>Use Fabuliner Liquid Eyeliner to apply a thin line from the inner to the outer corner of your lid along the upper and lower lash line.</p>\r\n<p>For a more dramatic look, make your line thicker and bolder. </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Tip: Extend slightly past the lash line for a sassy feline-flick!</p>', '890.00', '0.00', 6, 3, '', 'Fabuliner Liquid Eyeliner', '', 'FabulinerLiquid', 'Fabuliner Liquid Eyeliner', 3, 0, '2020-10-02 11:24:52', 0),
(408, 'FL', 23, 194, 19, 'Jordana Fineliner Felt-Tip Liquid Liner', '<p>Felt-tip liquid liner</p>\r\n<p>Lines, defines, accentuates</p>\r\n<p>Creates ultra-fine lines</p>\r\n<p>Glides on smooth and snag-free</p>\r\n<p>Quick drying formula</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>', 'Sometimes you need a perfectly lined look pronto but barely have enough time for breakfast before running out of the door! This felt-tip liner with a liquid finish is here to save the day! Creating ultra-fine lines has never been easier than with the quick-drying, lasts-all-day Fineliner Felt-Tip Liquid Liner!\r\n\r\n', '<p>Water (Aqua), Propylene Glycol, Triethanolamine, Oleyl Alcohol, Magnesium Aluminum Stearate, Stearic Acid, Glyceryl Stearate, Cellulose, Hectorite, Xanthum Gum, Acrylates/C10-30 Alkyl Acrylate Crosspolymer, Isopropylparaben, Butylparaben, Isobutylparaben.</p>\r\n<p>+/-May Contain: Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499).</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '<p>How To Apply: Use Fineliner Felt-tip Liner to apply a thin line from the inner to the outer corner of your lid along the upper and lower lash line. For a more dramatic look, make your line thicker and bolder.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '990.00', '0.00', 6, 4, '', ' Fineliner Felt-Tip Liquid Liner', '', 'Fineliner', ' Fineliner Felt-Tip Liquid Liner', 2, 0, '2020-10-02 11:33:28', 0),
(409, 'BFP', 23, 194, 19, ' Jordana Fabuliner Bold Felt-Tip Liquid Eyeliner', '<p>Felt-tip liquid eyeliner</p>\r\n<p>Lines, defines, accentuates</p>\r\n<p>Creates thick, bold lines</p>\r\n<p>Glides on smooth and snag-free</p>\r\n<p>Water-resistant, quick drying formula</p>\r\n<p>Made in Germany</p>', 'Bold lines are for bold girls! Fabuliner Bold Felt-tip Liquid Eyeliner is the ultimate rock-star liner with a thicker-than-normal felt tip. Defined eyes will never get lost in the crowd—and you\'ll never feel a snag while applying, or see a smear! You\'re in control!\r\n\r\n', '<p>Water (Aqua), Butylene Glycol, Alcohol, Glycerin, Black 2 (CI 77266), Polyacrylate-16, Disodium Cetyl Phenyl Ether Disulfonate, PEG/PPG-14/4 Dimethicone, PEG-14 Dimethicone, Phenoxyethanol, Dehydroacetic Acid, Caprylyl Glycol, Diethylhexyl Sodium Sulfosuccinate, Disodium Laureth Sulfosuccinate, Sodium Laureth-12 Sulfate.</p>', '<p>How to apply: Apply Fabuliner Bold Felt-tip Liquid Eyeliner starting at the inner corner of lid and move toward the outer corner. One swipe of this bold liner goes a long way!</p>', '1100.00', '0.00', 6, 4, '', ' Fabuliner Bold Felt-Tip Liquid Eyeliner', '', 'FabulinerBold', ' Fabuliner Bold Felt-Tip Liquid Eyeliner', 1, 0, '2020-10-02 16:32:38', 0),
(410, '1105189', 22, 157, 21, 'KEUNE CARE KERATIN SMOOTH MASQUE-500ML', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Keratin Smooth Mask is a rich moisturizing treatment that smoothes frizz, fluff and flyaways. Like its name says, it’s infused with keratin, a fibrous protein found in your hair and a key building block. This means this mask is perfect for dry or damaged hair. Peptides dive deep beneath the surface of each strand to restore damage, while keravis strengthens and helps prevent breakage</span></p>', 'This luxurious treatment enriches the hair with Keratin and Keravis, greatly improving its strength and adding beautiful shine.\r\nSuitable for\r\nResistant and damaged hair.', '', '', '5900.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281103943', 'HAIR MASQUE', '', 'HAIRMASK,HAIRMASQUE,KERATINSMOOTHMASQUE,KEUNEPRODUCTS', '', 1, 0, '2020-10-05 18:03:49', 0),
(411, '22EKTNEKU891', 22, 157, 21, 'KEUNE CARE COLOR BRILLIANZ MASK/MASQUE-200ML', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Colored hair tends to get dry, so treat it well to keep it looking luminous and salon-fresh. We&rsquo;ve got just the thing &mdash; Color Brillianz Mask is a moisturizing, soothing and strengthening mask designed especially for colored hair. Packed with ingredients to boost hair health and preserve your color, it&rsquo;s an essential weekly treat. Its Color Sealing Complex creates a protective barrier around each strand, which locks pigments in. Solamer UVA and UVB filters block out the sun&rsquo;s rays to keep your color from fading. Sunflower seed extract nourishes and neutralizes free radicals, which will extend the longevity of your color. Finally, silk proteins deeply moisturize, nourish and add luminous shine.</span></p>', 'An intensive caring mask for color-treated tresses. The Color Sealing Complex ensures long-lasting color brilliance, while the moisturizing, restoring formula repairs, protects and strengthens the hair.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nDamaged hair treated with anytype of artificial pigment.', '', '', '2780.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281103882', 'HAIR MASQUE', '', 'MASK,HAIRMASQUE,COLORBRILLIANZMASK,KEUNEPRODUCTS', '', 2, 0, '2020-10-05 18:17:05', 0),
(412, '1105188', 22, 157, 21, 'KEUNE CARE KERATIN SMOOTH MASK/MASQUE-200ML', '', 'This luxurious treatment enriches the hair with Keratin and Keravis, greatly improving its strength and adding beautiful shine.  \r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nResistant and damaged hair.', '', '', '3500.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281103899', 'HAIR MASK', '', 'HAIRMASK,MASQUE,KEUNEKERATINSMOOTHMASK,KEUNEPRODUCTS', '', 2, 0, '2020-10-05 18:22:52', 0),
(413, '1105187', 22, 157, 21, 'KEUNE CARE VITAL NUTRITION MASK/MASQUE-500ML', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">A rich, luxe, super nourishing mask perfect for dry, dull and damaged hair. Use once or twice a week to restore, revitalize and rehydrate stressed strands. After cleansing, towel dry, work through lengths and ends, indulge and rinse thoroughly. For extra TLC: wrap a warm towel around your head while Vital Nutrition Mask sinks in. Its rich formula is made with wheat proteins, keravis and a blend of five essential minerals so your hair is left feeling good and looking great: healthy, soft and shiny. Good for all hair types, this is a moisturizing must-have.</span></p>', 'A luxurious treatment that improves elasticity, soothes damaged strands, strengthens and adds shine.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nFragile, extremely dry and damaged hair.', '', '', '4425.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281103929', 'HAIR MASK/MASQUE', '', 'HAIRMASK,HAIRMASQUE,KEUNEVITALNUTRITIONMASK,MASQUE,KEUNEPRODUCTS', '', 2, 0, '2020-10-05 18:33:18', 0),
(414, '1105186', 22, 157, 21, 'KEUNE CARE VITAL NUTRITION MASK/MASQUE-200ML', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: #f3f3f3;\">A rich, luxe, super nourishing mask perfect for dry, dull and damaged hair. Use once or twice a week to restore, revitalize and rehydrate stressed strands. After cleansing, towel dry, work through lengths and ends, indulge and rinse thoroughly. For extra TLC: wrap a warm towel around your head while Vital Nutrition Mask sinks in. Its rich formula is made with wheat proteins, keravis and a blend of five essential minerals so your hair is left feeling good and looking great: healthy, soft and shiny. Good for all hair types, this is a moisturizing must-have.</span></p>', 'A luxurious treatment that improves elasticity, soothes damaged strands, strengthens and adds shine.\r\n\r\nSuitable for\r\nFragile, extremely dry and damaged hair.', '', '', '2650.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '8719281103875', 'HAIR MASK/MASQUE', '', 'HAIRMASK,HAIRMASQUE,MASK,KEUNEVITALNURITIONMASK,KEUNEPRODUCTS', '', 0, 0, '2020-10-05 18:41:41', 0),
