(416, 'MC-301', 23, 141, 19, 'Jordana Best Lash Extreme Volumizing Mascara', '<p>Full, lash-expanding look</p>\r\n<p>Evenly separates every lash</p>\r\n<p>Mega staying power</p>\r\n<p>Made in Italy</p>\r\n<p> </p>', 'Take your look from class to sass with lashes that love to flirt with volume! The dense-bristled brush picks up just the right amount of mascara, evenly coating and separating each lash for a pretty doe-eyed effect! Add an extra coat for unbelievable 3-D volume!\r\n\r\n', '<p>How to apply: Start at the root of lashes and wiggle the brush, sweeping Best Lash Extreme Volumizing Mascara upward in long, lifting strokes. Brush through bottom lashes for a doe-eyed effect! Apply another coat for maximum volume!</p>', '<p>Water (Aqua), Beeswax (Cera Alba), Iron Oxide (CI 77499), Copernicia Cerifera (Carnauba) Wax (Cera Carnauba), Cichorium Intybus (Chicory) Root Extract (Cichorium Intybus Root Extract), Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Wax (Helianthus Annuus Seed Wax), Stearic Acid, Palmitic Acid, Propanediol, Triethanolamine, Polyamide-5, Phenoxyethanol, Galactoarabinan, Caprylyl Glycol, Aminomethyl Propanediol, Potassium Sorbate, Caesalpinia Spinosa Gum, Acacia Senegal Gum (Acacia Senegal).</p>', '1990.00', '0.00', 6, 8, '', ' Best Lash Extreme Volumizing Mascara', '', 'VolumizingMascara', ' Best Lash Extreme Volumizing Mascara', 5, 0, '2020-10-07 18:26:00', 0),
(417, 'FPP', 23, 12, 19, 'Jordana Prime No-Pores Pore Refining Face Primer', '<p>Hydrates skin</p>\r\n<p>Reduces the look of large pores and redness</p>\r\n<p>Non-greasy feel</p>\r\n<p>Does not clog pores</p>\r\n<p>Extends the wear of makeup</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>', 'Prime all the time! Prime No-Pores Pore Refining Face Primer glides on easily and visibly reduces the look of large pores and redness, while hydrating skin.\r\n\r\nThe result is a radiant, fresh face and makeup that goes on smoother and lasts longer. The secret to perfectly polished skin is so simple—you\'ll never want to skip this step again!\r\n\r\n', '<p>Water (Aqua), Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Polymethylsilsesquioxane, Neopentyl Glycol Diheptanoate, Hydroxypropylcocoate PEG-8 Dimethicone, Isododecane, Dimethicone, Glycerine, Cyclopentasiloxane, Allantoin, Dimethicone/Vinyl Dimethicone Crosspolymer, Phenoxyethanol, Magnesium Sulfate, PEG/PPG-18/18 Dimethicone, Silica, Zea Mays (Corn) Starch, Ethylhexylglycerin, Menthone Glycerin Acetal, Disodium EDTA, BHT, Sodium Hydroxide, Sodium Hyaluronate.</p>', '<p>Apply a dime-sized amount of Prime No-Pores Pore Refining Face Primer with fingertips, beginning at the center of the face moving outward. Let dry before applying makeup, or wear alone for a fresh look.</p>', '1750.00', '0.00', 6, 8, '', 'Prime No-Pores Pore Refining Face Primer', '', 'FacePrimer', 'Prime No-Pores Pore Refining Face Primer', 4, 0, '2020-10-09 09:56:36', 0),
(418, 'LF', 23, 195, 19, 'Creamy Liquid Foundation', '<p>Medium-to-full coverage</p>\r\n<p>Oil-free formula</p>\r\n<p>Blends evenly on skin</p>\r\n<p>Suitable for all skin types</p>\r\n<p>Made in USA</p>\r\n<p> </p>', 'For a perfect \"woke up like this\" look, Creamy Liquid Foundation is not messing around on the flawless front! The oil-free formula fights shine and conceals problem areas like no other. Rock Insta-ready skin with #nofilter!\r\n\r\n', '<p>Water (Aqua), Propylene Glycol, PEG-8, Isopropyl Isostearate, Ethylhexyl Palmitate, Stearic Acid, Isostearyl Neopentanoate, Talc, Glyceryl Stearate, Cetyl Acetate, Diethylhexyl Adipate, Magnesium Aluminum Silicate, PEG-20 Methyl Glucose Sesquistearate, Methyl Glucose Sesquistearate, Imidazolidinyl Urea, Lanolin Alcohol, Lecithin, Cocoyl Sarcosine, Cellulose Gum, Methylparaben, Ethylhexyl Stearate, Potassium Hydroxide, Acetylated Lanolin Alcohol, Allantoin, Propylparaben, Tocopherol, Panthenol. +/- May Contain: Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891), Iron Oxides (CI 77491, CI 77492, CI 77499)</p>', '<p>Choose a shade of Creamy Liquid Foundation that is closest to your natural skin tone. Press down gently on the no mess-no drip pump to collect a small amount of foundation. Apply foundation to the center of your face and blend in an outward motion. Be sure to blend into your jawline and neck area for a seamless, natural look!</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Tip: Sweep on Perfect Pressed Powder after foundation to lock in your look and control shine throughout the day.</p>', '690.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', 'Creamy Liquid Foundation', '', 'LiquidFoundation', 'Creamy Liquid Foundation', 10, 0, '2020-10-09 12:06:10', 0),
