(424, '1105178', 22, 90, 21, 'KEUNE CARE DERMA ACTIVATE SHAMPOO ', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">In many cases, hair loss can be prevented by using products that stimulate the scalp&rsquo;s metabolism. That&rsquo;s what Derma Activate Shampoo does for you. Vitamin H improves the quality of the keratin inside your hair, which are like building blocks. Stronger keratin means stronger hair that&rsquo;s less likely to fall out. Keep using Derma Activate Shampoo and with time, your hair will be thicker, more voluminous and your scalp will function better.</span></p>', 'This rejuvenating shampoo is best suited to those with sensitive scalps and fine, thinning hair. Essential Minerals in combination with Vitamin H prevent the early stages of hair loss.', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Water, Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Sodium Chloride, Disodium Cocomphadiacetate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glycol Distearate, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, PEG-200 Hydrogenated Glyceryl Palmate, Propylene Glycol, Panthenol, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Cocamide MEA, Fragrrfance, Glyceryl Laurate, PEG-7 Glyceryl Cocoate, Diazolidinyl Urea, Tetrasodium EDTA, methylparaben, laureth-10, Citric Acid, Polyquaternium-7, Sodium Cocoyl HydrolyzedWheat Protein, Propylparaben, Saccharomyces/Magnesium Ferment, Saccharomyces/Iron Ferment, Biotin, Saccharomyces/Zinc Ferment, Saccharomyces/Copper Ferment, Saccharomyces.Silicon Ferment, Linalool, Limonene, Hexyl Cinnamal</span></p>', '', '1710.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103417', 'KEUNE CARE DERMA ACTIVATE SHAMPOO ', '', '', 'KEUNECAREDERMAACTIVATESHAMPOO ', 1, 0, '2020-10-28 15:21:01', 0),
(425, '1105177', 22, 90, 21, 'KEUNE CARE ABSOLUTE VOLUME SHAMPOO ', '<p><span style=\"color: #3c3c3b; font-family: \'Futura PT W10 Book\', \'Futura PT W02 Book\', \'Futura PT Book\', Futura, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Big is beautiful. And to give you the biggest, most beautiful hair, we made Absolute Volume. Enriched with moisturizing, thickening provitamin B5, plumping and strengthening wheat proteins, it lifts your hair up where it belongs without adding weight.</span></p>', 'A gentle cleansing shampoo that builds volume without making the hair heavy. Provitamin B5 and Wheat Proteins strengthen and thicken the hair structure.', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;\">Water, Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Decyl Glucoside, Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Sodium Chloride, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Panthenol, Propylene Glycol, PEG-200 Hydrogenated Glyceryl Palmate, Fragrance, PEG-40 Hydrogenated Castor Oil, Tetrasodium EDTA, Polyquaternium-10, Glyceryl Laurate, Diazolidinyl Urea, PEG-7Glyceryl Cocoate, Citric Acid, Methylparaben, Sodium Cocoyl Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, propylparaben, Saccharomyces/ Copper Ferment, Saccharomyces/ Silicone Ferment, Linalool, Citronellol, Coumarin, Geraniol, Limonene</span></p>', '', '1590.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103417', 'KEUNECAREABSOLUTEVOLUMESHAMPOO ', '', 'KEUNECAREABSOLUTEVOLUMESHAMPOO', 'KEUNECAREABSOLUTEVOLUMESHAMPOO', 0, 0, '2020-10-28 15:31:33', 0);
