(494, '2237018', 22, 45, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC MINT CLEANSER', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">I am 100% free of sodium lauryl sulfate, parabens, petrochemicals, alcohol, phathalates, artificial fragrance and colour I am a soap free cleanser that gently sloughs away the day\'s dirt, grime and make up. I am a boon for oily and acne prone skin. Enriched with the powerful combination of antibacterial and antiseptic extracts of clove and spearmint, I help control the excess oil secretion from the skin. Included in my formulation is zinc oxide, which effectively heals acne while jojoba and neem seed oils regulate the oil level in the skin. The blend of rose, tea tree leaf, peppermint and geranium essential oils prevents the skin from drying out, leaving your skin calm, moist and renewed.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Benefits:<br /></strong><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Deep cleanses and refreshes<br /></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Heals acne<br /></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Control the excess oil secretion from the skin<br /></span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Prevents the skin from drying out, leaving your skin calm, moist and renewed</span></p>', '', '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\">Essential oils of peppermint, chinaberry seed, jojoba seed, geranium and damask rose</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-size: 12pt;\">Extracts of spearmint and cloves</span></p>', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px 40px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Dampen skin, take a little cleanser with water and massage onto face using circular strokes.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Wipe off with damp cotton.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Use it every morning and night.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Follow it up with Aromatic Skin Toner.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '785.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8904089804912', 'AROMA MAGIC MINT CLEANSER', '', 'AROMAMAGICMINTCLEANSER', 'AROMA MAGIC MINT CLEANSER', 3, 0, '2020-11-10 11:45:37', 0),
(496, '2222063', 22, 48, 36, 'STIVES ACNE CONTROL APRICOT SCRUB-170G', '<p>This multi-award winner contains 100% natural walnut shell powder and naturally sourced apricot extract. Uncover super smoothness as it deeply exfoliates for clean, glowing skin.</p>', '', '<p>Medicinal Ingredient: Salicylic Acid 2%Non-Medicinal Ingredients: Aqua, Juglans Regia (Walnut) Shell Powder, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Glycerin, Cetearyl Alcohol, Zea Mays (Corn) Kernel Meal, Cetyl Alcohol, Triethanolamine, Sodium Lauryl Sulfoacetate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glyceryl Stearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Cetyl Acetate, Benzyl Alcohol, Carbomer, Ceteareth-20, Acetylated Lanolin Alcohol, Polysorbate 60, Parfum, Disodium EDTA, Benzoic Acid, Sorbic Acid, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Fruit Extract, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891).</p>', '<p>Apply product to a small area once a day for three days to test if you are sensitive to this product. If no discomfort occurs, dispense scrub onto fingertips and massage onto damp skin. Spread in small circular motions, then rinse and glow! Start with one application daily, then gradually increase to two or three times daily, if needed. If dryness or peeling occurs, reduce application to once a day or every other day. Do not use if inner seal/foil is missing or broken.</p>', '1050.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '077043104507', '', '', 'STIVESBLEMSIHCONTROLAPRICOTSCRUB,FACESCRUB,APRICOTSCRUB,STIVESPRODUCT', '', 4, 0, '2020-11-10 12:30:56', 0),
(497, '2263082', 22, 48, 36, 'ST IVES FRESH SKIN APRICOT SCRUB-170G', '<p>This multi-award winner contains 100% natural walnut shell powder and naturally sourced apricot extract. Uncover super smoothness as it deeply exfoliates for clean, glowing skin.</p>', '', '<p>Aqua, Juglans Regia (Walnut) Shell Powder, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Glycerin, Cetearyl Alcohol, Zea Mays (Corn) Kernel Meal, Cetyl Alcohol, Sodium Lauryl Sulfoacetate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glyceryl stearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Cetyl Acetate, Benzyl alcohol, Ceteareth-20, Acetylated Lanolin Alcohol, Carbomer, Polysorbate 60, Triethanolamine, Parfum, Disodium EDTA, Benzoic Acid, Sorbic Acid, Prunus Armeniaca (Apricot) Fruit Extract, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891).</p>', '<p>Squeeze a dime sized amount of Fresh Skin Apricot Scrub onto your fingertips and massage onto damp skin.</p>\r\n<p>Spread in small circular motions, applying gentle pressure to wake your skin’s natural circulation.</p>\r\n<p>Work all over, right up to your hairline and onto the sides of your nose.</p>\r\n<p>When you’re done, rinse and pat dry with a clean towel.</p>\r\n<p>Use 3 to 4 times a week (depending on skin) for best results.</p>', '1050.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '077043103609', 'FACE SCRUB', '', 'STIVESFRESHSKINAPRICOTSCRUB,STIVEPRODUCT,FACESCRUB', '', 1, 0, '2020-11-10 12:47:48', 0),
(498, '2222106', 22, 48, 36, 'ST IVES ENERGIZING COCONUT & COFFE SCRUB-170G', '<p>Squeeze a dime sized amount of Energizing Coconut & Coffee Face Scrub onto your fingertips and massage onto damp skin.</p>\r\n<p>Spread in small circular motions, applying gentle pressure to wake your skin’s natural circulation.</p>\r\n<p>Work all over, right up to your hairline and onto the sides of your nose.</p>\r\n<p>When you’re done, rinse and pat dry with a clean towel.</p>\r\n<p>Use 3 to 4 times a week (depending on skin) for best results.</p>', '', '<p>Water (Aqua), Juglans Regia (Walnut) Shell Powder, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Glycerin, Cetearyl Alcohol, Zea Mays (Corn) Kernel Meal, Cetyl Alcohol, Sodium Lauryl Sulfoacetate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Glyceryl Stearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Cetyl Acetate, Benzyl Alcohol, Fragrance (Parfum), Ceteareth-20, Triethanolamine, Carbomer, Polysorbate 60, Disodium EDTA, Benzoic Acid, Acetylated Lanolin Alcohol, Sorbic Acid, Caffeine, Cocos Nucifera (Coconut) Fruit Extract, Caramel, Titanium Dioxide (CI 77891).</p>', '<p>Squeeze a dime sized amount of Energizing Coconut & Coffee Face Scrub onto your fingertips and massage onto damp skin.</p>\r\n<p>Spread in small circular motions, applying gentle pressure to wake your skin’s natural circulation.</p>\r\n<p>Work all over, right up to your hairline and onto the sides of your nose.</p>\r\n<p>When you’re done, rinse and pat dry with a clean towel.</p>\r\n<p>Use 3 to 4 times a week (depending on skin) for best results.</p>', '1050.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '077043000168', 'FACE SCRUB', '', 'STIVESENERGIZINGCOCONUTCOFFESCRUB,STIVEPRODUCT,FACESCRUB', '', 0, 0, '2020-11-10 12:53:39', 0),
(499, '2237070', 22, 167, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC CARROT SUN LOTION', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">I am 100 % free of oxybenzone, paraben, harsh chemicals, alcohol and artificial fragrance. My all-mineral, super light formula creates a physical barrier between you and the sun. I am non greasy, skin friendly and enriched with carrotseed, sea buckthorn and rice bran oils. They provide natural sun safety, vitamins B5, C, E and prevent visible signs of ageing. Notes of lavender, chamomile and myrrh essential oils moisturise, soothe and protect your skin. The non-nano zinc oxide in me is a mineral reflector found in nature that scatters harmful rays. Carrot extracts fortify skin cells and provide smart sun protection.</span></p>', '', '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Essential oils of lavender, chamomile and myrrh</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Non nano zinc oxide</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Extracts of carrots and aloe vera</span></p>', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px 40px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Apply generously on your face and body 15 minutes before sun exposure for desired protection.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Reapply every 90 minutes and 30 minutes after swimming and continuous exposure in the sun.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Use a moisturiser appropriate to your skin type before using the sunscreen gel. This perfectly complements the daily makeup too.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '550.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103455', 'AROMA MAGIC CARROT SUN LOTION', '', 'AROMAMAGICCARROTSUNLOTION', 'AROMA MAGIC CARROT SUN LOTION', 1, 0, '2020-11-10 12:54:55', 0),
(500, '2237053', 22, 122, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC BRIGHTENING LOTION', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\">I am 100% free of parabens, harsh chemicals, alcohol, artificial fragrance and colour. Extracts of triphla, amla and witch hazel detoxify, treat sunburns and lighten your complexion while balancing the pH level and uneven skin tone. Oils of nutmeg, clove and garlic are effective antiseptic agents that prevent and treat skin infections. Vitamin C and natural AHA are valuable components that gently exfoliate the dead & dull skin cells to make your skin bright and radiant.</p>', '', '<p>Extracts of Chebulic Myrobalan, Amla, triphala and witch hazel extract</p>\r\n<p>Oils of cloves, garlic and nutmeg</p>', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px 40px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Mix this lotion with Tan Removing Milk Pack to make a paste</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Apply a layer evenly on face and neck, and leave on for 15-20 minutes</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Wipe or rinse off gently with water</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Use twice a week for best results</li>\r\n</ul>', '810.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8904089803328', 'AROMA MAGIC BRIGHTENING LOTION', '', 'AROMAMAGICBRIGHTENINGLOTION', 'AROMA MAGIC BRIGHTENING LOTION', 2, 0, '2020-11-10 13:03:05', 0),
(501, '2237021', 22, 104, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC SKIN TONER', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\">I am 100% free of alcohol, parabens, petrochemicals, phthalates, artificial fragrance, and colour. I am a special formulation intended to clean and tone the skin without drying it. Extracts of pomegranate together with lavender and peppermint heals the skin and renews the skin cells and increases its circulation. Witch Hazel prevents moisture loss while the essential oils of rosemary and ylang-ylang act as natural astringents that calms and balances the skin, delivering vital nutrients and vitamins to it. You will find your skin looking healthier and toned.</p>', '', '<p>Pomegranate Juice</p>\r\n<p>Witch Hazel</p>\r\n<p>Essential oils of Rosemary and Ylang-Ylang</p>', '<p>Spray onto face directly or on a small piece of cotton and dab onto face.</p>\r\n<p>Avoid the eye area.</p>\r\n<p>Use in the morning and night after cleansing.</p>\r\n<p>Follow it up with the Oily Skin Oil.</p>', '680.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103486', 'AROMA MAGIC SKIN TONER', '', 'AROMAMAGICSKINTONER', 'AROMA MAGIC SKIN TONER', 2, 0, '2020-11-10 13:18:45', 0),
(502, '2263080', 22, 48, 36, 'ST IVES BLACKHEAD CLEARING GREEN TEA SCRUB-170G', '<p>This scrub contains 100% naturally sourced exfoliant and green tea extract. Experience the satisfaction as it unclogs dirt and oil from pores for clear, radiant skin</p>', '', '<p><strong style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: center; text-shadow: none !important; box-shadow: none !important; outline: none !important;\">Medicinal Ingredient:</strong><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\"> Salicylic Acid 1%</span><strong style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: center; text-shadow: none !important; box-shadow: none !important; outline: none !important;\">Non-Medicinal Ingredients:</strong><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\"> Aqua, Hydrated Silica, Glycerin, Glyceryl Stearate SE, Cetearyl Alcohol, Sodium Lauryl Sulfoacetate, Cocamidopropyl Betaine, Cetyl Alcohol, Triethanolamine, Glyceryl Stearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Cetyl Acetate, Benzyl Alcohol, Parfum, Carbomer, Acetylated Lanolin Alcohol, Ceteareth-20, Polysorbate 60, Propylene Glycol, Disodium EDTA, Benzoic Acid, Sorbic Acid,Olea Europaea (Olive) Leaf Extract, Camellia Sinensis Leaf Extract, Red 33 (CI 17200), Blue 1 (CI 42090), Yellow 5 (CI 19140).</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: bold; text-align: center;\"> Apply product to a small area once a day for three days to test if you are sensitive to this product. If no discomfort occurs, dispense scrub onto fingertips and massage onto damp skin. Spread in small circular motions, then rinse and glow! Start with one application daily, then gradually increase to two or three times daily, if needed. If dryness or peeling occurs, reduce application to once a day or every other day. Do not use if inner seal/foil is missing or broken.</span></p>', '1050.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '077043358023', 'FACE SCRUB', '', 'STIVESBLACKHEADCLEARINGGREENTEASCRUB,STIVEPRODUCT,FACESCRUB', 'ST IVES BLACKHEAD CLEARING GREEN TEA SCRUB-170G', 2, 0, '2020-11-10 13:22:58', 0),
(503, '2237063', 22, 122, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC ALMOND LOTION', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">I am 100% free of petrochemicals, phathalates, toxic ingredients, parabens, artificial fragrance and colour. Enriched with SPF 15, I protect, moisturise and rejuvenate your skin. The revitalising extracts of almond fruit and lotus leaf seal in the moisture imparting instant relief to dry and delicate skin. The combination of wheat germ and jojoba oils together with mango seed butter effectively repair and soothe dry and damaged skin. My potent blend of patchouli, geranium and rose essential oils revives the skin leaving it with a lustrous and healthy texture.</span></p>', '', '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Extracts of almond fruit and lotus leaf</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Oils of wheat germ and jojoba</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Essential oils of patchouli, geranium and rose</span></p>', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px 40px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Gently massage the moisturiser onto your skin</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Use daily after cleansing, toning & oiling the skin, morning and night</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Use as frequently as the skin needs some extra care</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '1395.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8904089804363', 'AROMA MAGIC ALMOND LOTION', '', 'AROMAMAGICALMONDLOTION', 'V', 1, 0, '2020-11-10 13:23:26', 0),
(504, '2237043', 22, 113, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC UNDER EYE CREAM', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">I am 100% free from parabens, petrochemicals, phtalates, toxic ingredients, artificial colouring and fragrances. The calcium and zinc present in goji berry fruit extracts nourish and minimise wrinkles. The olive butter oil together with rice bran oil repair and lighten your skin with Vitamin C. The anti-aging union of essential oils of lavender, rosemary, and seabuckthorn support new cell formation in your skin. Combined with extracts of hibiscus, I leave your skin fresh and youthful.</span></p>', '', '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Extracts of goji berry and hibiscus</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Oils of olive butter and rice bran</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Essential oils of lavender, rosemary, and seabuckthorn</span></p>', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px 40px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Apply around the eyes and massage gently with a fingertip.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Use every morning and night.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '785.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8904089805230', 'AROMA MAGIC UNDER EYE CREAM', '', 'AROMAMAGICUNDEREYECREAM', 'AROMA MAGIC UNDER EYE CREAM', 1, 0, '2020-11-10 14:18:56', 0),
(505, '2237044', 22, 113, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC UNDER EYE GEL', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">I am 100% free from parabens, petrochemicals, phtalates, toxic ingredients, artificial colouring, and fragrances. My hydrating fusion of cucumber extracts and aloe vera gel refreshes your skin, while the exotic extracts of horsetail & green tea complemented by gotu kola act as powerful antioxidant agents that firm and tighten your delicate skin. I am rich in essential oils of lavender and lemon that soothe puffy eyes and lighten the skin around the eyes and lips.</span></p>', '', '<p>Extracts of cucumber, horsetail and green tea</p>\r\n<p>Aloe vera gel</p>\r\n<p>Essential oils of lavender and lemon</p>', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px 40px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Apply around the eyes and massage gently with a fingertip.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Use every morning and night.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '785.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103486', 'AROMA MAGIC UNDER EYE GEL', '', 'AROMAMAGICUNDEREYEGEL', 'AROMA MAGIC UNDER EYE GEL', 2, 0, '2020-11-10 14:24:01', 0),
(506, '2237101', 22, 133, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC SKIN OIL', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\">Fairy skin oil prevents, acne and pimples. It brings down inflammation and blackheads.  It is a blend of witch hazel extracts and Jojoba oil and essential oils of Tea tree, Juniper berry and mint. This blend of oils prevents acne and pimples, balances sebum, reduces blackheads and inflammation.</p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\">The Witch Hazel extracts help to fight acne and Jojoba oil maintains the skin hydrated, nourished and moisturized. The essential oils of Tea tree help in treating bacterial and fungal skin conditions, Juniper berry acts as a natural skin toner and reduces skin blemishes and Mint brightens dull skin, controls excess oil and revive the youthful freshness of your skin. </p>', 'Fairy skin oil prevents, acne and pimples. It brings down inflammation and blackheads. ', '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Witch Hazel extracts</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Jojoba Oil</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Essential oils of Tea Tree | Juniper Berry | mint</span></p>', '<ul>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Apply 4-5 drops onto your clean face and neck every morning and night.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '2025.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8904089804011', 'AROMA MAGIC SKIN OIL', '', 'AROMAMAGICSKINOIL', 'AROMA MAGIC SKIN OIL', 2, 0, '2020-11-10 14:30:01', 0),
(507, '2237091', 22, 105, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC FACE CONCENTRATE', '<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.375px; line-height: 1.6; font-size: 15px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; text-size-adjust: 100%; text-rendering: optimizespeed; margin: 0px 0px 25px;\">I am 100% free of parabens, petrochemicals, sulphates, alcohol, toxic ingredients, artificial colouring and fragrance. Powered by the potent blend of essential oils of rosemary, lemon and chamomile infused water; I lighten blemishes, dark spots and pigmentation patches on the face and body. Radish root extract and vitamin B12 in my formula helps to protect the skin from sun damage and free radicals, leaving it clearer and prevents the formation of future dark spots.</p>', '', '<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Orange and rosemary infused Water</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Vegetable glycerine</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Essential oils of cypress and tea tree</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Extracts of mangosteen</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Tocopherol</span></p>', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 25px 40px; padding: 0px; text-rendering: optimizelegibility; font-family: Lato, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 0.375px;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Clean skin with Aroma Magic face wash. Blot dry with a tissue.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Apply Aroma Anti-Pigmentation Concentrate all over the face. Allow absorption.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Apply Anti-Acne Serum on affected areas and leave it on.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Apply Aloe Vera sunscreen gel when going out in the sun.</li>\r\n</ul>', '315.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '2237091', 'AROMA MAGIC FACE CONCENTRATE', '', 'AROMAMAGICFACECONCENTRATE', 'AROMA MAGIC FACE CONCENTRATE', 5, 0, '2020-11-10 14:48:57', 0),
(508, '2263074', 22, 122, 36, ' ST.IVES REVITALIZING  ACAI BLUEBERRY & CHIA SEED OIL BODY LOTION-621ML', '<p>Superfoods aren’t only for your smoothies! Give your skin a wakeup call with our Revitalizing Açai, Blueberry & Chia Seed Oil Body Lotion! Made With 100% natural moisturizers like soybean oil and glycerin, this non-greasy lotion absorbs quickly to revitalize tired skin and gives it a boost of instant hydration for a lit-from-within glow!</p>', '', '<p>Water (Aqua), Glycerin, Stearic Acid, Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil, Glycol Stearate, Dimethicone, Glyceryl Stearate, Triethanolamine, Caprylyl Glycol, Cetyl Alcohol, Phenoxyethanol, Fragrance (Parfum), Carbomer, Hydroxyethylcellulose, Disodium EDTA, BHT, Stearamide AMP, Salvia Hispanica Seed Oil, Euterpe Oleracea Fruit Extract, Maltodextrin, Vaccinium Myrtillus Fruit Extract.</p>', '<p>Press 1-2 pumps of Revitalizing Acai, Blueberry & Chia Seed Oil Body Lotion into palms and smooth all over, concentrating on extra-dry spots like elbows and heels.</p>\r\n<p>Massage lotion in until absorbed. Use daily. *Pro-tip*: Awaken your skin by massaging in the lotion in small circles to boost blood flow!</p>', '2200.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '077043000212', '', '', 'STIVESREVITALIZINGBLUEBERRYSEEDBODYLOTION,BODYLOTION,STIVESPRODUCT', ' ST.IVES REVITALIZING  ACAI BLUEBERRY & CHIA SEED OIL BODY LOTION-621ML', 1, 0, '2020-11-10 16:53:36', 0),
(509, '2237115', 22, 122, 60, 'AROMA MAGIC PAPAYA LOTION', '<p><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">An antidote for oily and acne prone skin containing natural enzymes that remove black and white heads. brown spots and sebum deposit. works effectively as deep pore clenser before galvanic treatments.</span></p>', '', '<p>Extracts of apple</p>\r\n<p>Lemon</p>\r\n<p>Whey</p>\r\n<p>Pepin</p>\r\n<p>Bromalin</p>\r\n<p>Lactic and malic acids</p>', '<ul>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Mix enough lotion with 1 pouch of enzyme peel pack to make a paste.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Apply onto face avoiding the eye area.</span></li>\r\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Keep for 15 minutes and remove with damp cotton.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', '1990.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '2237115', 'AROMA MAGIC PAPAYA LOTION', '', 'AROMAMAGICPAPAYALOTION', 'AROMA MAGIC PAPAYA LOTION', 1, 0, '2020-11-10 18:37:44', 0),
