(512, '2263090', 22, 125, 36, 'ST.IVES PAMPERING VANILLA BODY WASH-400ML', '<p>Treat yourself to this rich, decadent body wash for soft, silky smooth skin. With 100% natural vanilla, oatmeal and soymilk extract, this body wash pampers for a luxurious cleanse.</p>', '', '<p>Water (Eau), Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Sodium Chloride, Cocamide MEA, Glycol Stearate, Fragrance (Parfum), Citric Acid, Sodium Benzoate, Glycerin, Tetrasodium EDTA, Stearamide AMP, Vanilla Planifolia Fruit Extract, PPG-9, Caramel, Avena Sativa (Oat) Meal Extract, Soymilk, Benzyl Alcohol, Benzyl Salicylate, Coumarin, Hexyl Cinnamal, Limonene, Linalool, Yellow 6 (CI 15985), Yellow 5 (CI 19140).</p>', '<p>Pour a generous amount of body wash onto your hands or favorite squishy pouf!</p>\r\n<p>Lather over wet skin, soaking up the incredible scent.When you’re done, rinse off!4. Enjoy skin that feels smooth all over!</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '1520.00', '0.00', 3, 1, '077043101582', 'BODY WASH', '', 'STIVESPAMPERINGVANILLABODYWASH,PAMPERINGBODYWASH,VANILLABODYWASH,STIVESPRODUCT', 'ST.IVES PAMPERING VANILLA BODY WASH-400ML', 2, 0, '2020-11-11 12:24:08', 0),
