(628, '1067011', 22, 139, 72, 'COLOSSAL BOLD LINER', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\">Maybelline New York\'s Colossal Bold Liner is a smudge-proof and waterproof long-lasting eyeliner that lasts up to 24 hours. The long handle and brush tip applicator make it easy to create sharp precise lines for different looks. From simple lines to dramatic winged eyeliner, the Colossal Bold Liner is perfect for daily use.</p>', '', '', '<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: #666666; font-family: \'Neue Helvetica W01\'; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.75px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: left;\">  </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Step 1. Starting at the inner corner of each eye , draw a neat stroke along your upper lash line.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 12.0pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 115%;\">Step 2. Extend a little beyond the outer corner of each eye to make an impact that lasts 24 hours.</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: #666666; font-family: \'Neue Helvetica W01\'; font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 1.75px; white-space: pre-line; background-color: #fafafa; text-align: left;\">  </p>', '1390.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8901526561681', 'COLOSSAL BOLD LINER', '', 'COLOSSALBOLDLINER', 'COLOSSAL BOLD LINER', 3, 0, '2020-12-14 18:09:05', 0),
