(694, '2228026', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON SPECIAL SALON PACK CONDITIONER', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: \'Verdana\',\'sans-serif\'; color: black; background: white;\">Dreamron conditioner with orange extract & vitamins is specially formulated to maintain the moisture & balance of oil in the hair. The conditioner replaces the lost moisture & oil during daily routines and provides extra nourishment. The additional moisturizers available, prevents the scalp & hair from drying, leaving it healthy shiny & manageable. The damages caused by UV rays are cut down to a large extent with the microfilm, which is provided by the conditioner. <span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"> </span></span></p>', '', '', '<p>After shampooing, gently massage into your hair. Leave for 2-3 minutes. Then rinse well.</p>', '750.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000732367', 'DREAMRON SPECIAL SALON PACK CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONSPECIALSALONPACKCONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON SPECIAL SALON PACK CONDITIONER', 2, 0, '2020-12-19 12:50:30', 0),
(695, '2223001', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON ALOE VERA SHAMPOO ', '<p><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c; font-family: Montserrat, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">Designed specifically for normal hair. This unique formula cleanses your hair without removing any of its natural balances. The Aloe Vera extract rich in a multitude of nutrients help add moisture to hair and prevents dryness, giving you soft, smooth, shiny and healthy hair.</span></p>', '', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c; font-family: Montserrat, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">Apply sufficient amount to wet hair and gently massage into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if desired. Then use Dreamron Aloe Vera Conditioner.</span></p>', '325.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103417', 'DREAMRON ALOE VERA SHAMPOO ', '', 'DREAMRONALOEVERASHAMPOO', 'DREAMRON ALOE VERA SHAMPOO ', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 12:05:14', 0),
(696, '2228008', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON AMLA EXTRACT SHAMPOO ', '<p>The best remedy to cleanse oily hair without disturbing its natural moisture or oil balance. The high levels of Vitamin C, amino acids and minerals found in Amla extract provide rich nourishment and strengthens your hair while preventing hair loss, breakage and premature graying. For healthy, shiny hair with enhanced color.</p>', '', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c; font-family: Montserrat, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">Apply sufficient amount to wet hair and gently massage into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if desired. Then use Dreamron Amla Extract Conditioner.</span></p>', '310.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730868', 'DREAMRON AMLA EXTRACT SHAMPOO ', '', 'DREAMRONAMLAEXTRACTSHAMPOO', 'DREAMRON AMLA EXTRACT SHAMPOO ', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 12:23:52', 0),
(697, '2228011', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON ANTI- BREAKAGE SHAMPOO ', '<p>Specifically designed to provide high damage resistance and strengthen hair against breakage and spilt ends. Rich in Grape Seed extract, a natural UV protector and Ginseng extract that nourishes the roots and prevents hair loss. This unique formula is also equipped with Vitamin E and Pro-Vitamin B5 to retain moisture and give you healthy, soft &amp; shiny hair.</p>', '', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c; font-family: Montserrat, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">Apply sufficient amount to wet hair and gently massage into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if desired. Then use Dreamron Anti - Breakage Conditioner.</span></p>', '320.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000731728', 'DREAMRON ANTI- BREAKAGE SHAMPOO ', '', 'DREAMRONANTIBREAKAGESHAMPOO', 'DREAMRON ANTI- BREAKAGE SHAMPOO ', 3, 0, '2020-12-21 12:28:02', 0),
(698, '2228013', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON ANTI- DANDRUFF SHAMPOO ', '<p>A special herbal formula that comes with 3 unique benefits – cleansing, conditioning and dandruff control. Active natural ingredients Lime &amp; Fenugreek extract along with added anti-dandruff agent directly attack the fungi that causes the formation of dandruff, while the nutrients in the Shampoo bring out the natural glow in your hair, leaving it healthy, soft and dandruff-free.</p>', '', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c; font-family: Montserrat, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">Apply sufficient amount to wet hair and gently massage into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if desired. </span></p>', '375.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000731049', 'DREAMRON ANTI- DANDRUFF SHAMPOO ', '', 'DREAMRONANTIDANDRUFFSHAMPOO', 'DREAMRON ANTI- DANDRUFF SHAMPOO ', 0, 0, '2020-12-21 12:32:37', 0),
(699, '2223005', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON KING COCONUT SHAMPOO ', '<p>Being a natural re-vitalizer the main ingredient King Coconut, gently cleanses dry and damaged hair preventing breakage, spilt ends and further hair damage. It increases hair growth while enhancing its natural color and retains moisture. The nutritious properties of the oil strengthen your hair making it soft and add extra shine.</p>', '', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #4c4c4c; font-family: Montserrat, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.3px;\">Apply sufficient amount to wet hair and gently massage into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if desired. Then use Dreamron King Coconut Conditioner.</span></p>', '325.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730882', 'DREAMRON KING COCONUT SHAMPOO', '', 'DREAMRONKINGCOCONUTSHAMPOO', 'DREAMRON KING COCONUT SHAMPOO', 0, 0, '2020-12-21 12:52:29', 0),
(700, '2223003', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON ALOE VERA CONDITIONER', '<p>A rejuvenating formula that protects the levels of moisture and oil content in normal hair. The Aloe Vera extract which is a natural conditioner, increases hair growth while repairing and restoring damaged hair. Enriched with nutrients to give you smooth, lustrous and manageable hair.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply evenly after shampooing and leave for 2-3 minutes. <br />Rinse well.</p>', '325.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730851', 'DREAMRON ALOE VERA CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONALOEVERACONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON ALOE VERA CONDITIONER', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 12:57:39', 0),
(701, '2228010', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON AMLA EXTRACT CONDITIONER', '<p>A specially formulated conditioner to treat oily hair. The Amla extract rich in natural conditioning agents helps maintain the moisture and oil content of hair while enhancing color and making your hair stronger. Reduces hair loss, breakage and untimely graying, leaving hair healthy and shiny.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply evenly after shampooing and leave for 2-3 minutes. Rinse well.</p>', '325.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730875', 'DREAMRON AMLA EXTRACT CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONAMLAEXTRACTCONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON AMLA EXTRACT CONDITIONER', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 13:00:44', 0),
(702, '2228012', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON ANTI- BREAKAGE CONDITIONER', '<p>Strengthens the hair giving it high damage resistance by restoring natural moisture and oil content. Active ingredients Grape seed extract acts as a natural UV protector, Ginseng extract nourishes, retains moisture, leaving you with strong and healthy hair without breakages or split ends.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply evenly after shampooing and leave for 2-3 minutes. <br />Rinse well.</p>', '320.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000731742', 'DREAMRON ANTI- BREAKAGE CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONANTIBREAKAGECONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON ANTI- BREAKAGE CONDITIONER', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 13:04:01', 0),
(703, '2228007', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON KING COCONUT CONDITIONER', '<p>Specially formulated to rejuvenate dry and damaged hair by restoring moisture with natural nutrients. The active ingredient King Coconut Oil helps maintain natural color brightness keeping hair soft, silky and shiny. Your ideal Conditioner to prevent hair loss and split ends while gently repairing the damage caused by daily maintenance.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply evenly after shampooing and leave for 2-3 minutes. <br />Rinse well.</p>', '310.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730899', 'DREAMRON KING COCONUT CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONKINGCOCONUTCONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON KING COCONUT CONDITIONER', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 13:06:09', 0),
(704, '2228018', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON KERATIN HAIR CONDITIONER', '<p>The Conditioner enriched with Keratin & Argan Oil infuses the keratin & moisture to the hair while strengthening and enhancing the natural shine. It makes hair strong and reduces hair breakages, damages, & split ends leaving them healthy & lively.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply evenly after shampooing and leave for 2-3 minutes. Rinse well.</p>', '525.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000731933', 'DREAMRON KERATIN HAIR CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONKERATINHAIRCONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON KERATIN HAIR CONDITIONER', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 13:33:20', 0),
(705, '2228017', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON KERATIN HAIR SHAMPOO', '<p>The Shampoo enriched with Keratin and Argan Oil strengthens the hair &amp; enhances the shine while cleansing the hair &amp; scalp gently. It effectively replaces the loss and damaged keratin from the hair leaving it strong &amp; resilient. Argan Oil moisturizes &amp; nourishes the hair keeping it healthy, shiny and bouncy.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply sufficient amount to wet hair and gently massage into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if desired. Then use Dreamron Keratin Hair Conditioner.</p>', '525.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000731926', 'DREAMRON KERATIN HAIR SHAMPOO', '', 'DREAMRONKERATINHAIRSHAMPOO', 'DREAMRON KERATIN HAIR SHAMPOO', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 13:39:07', 0),
(706, '2228019', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON CURL PROTECTIVE SHAMPOO ', '<p>The ultimate curl protective formula that restores damage done during the curling process while controlling frizziness. Free of SLES, it cleanses gently preserving the balance of natural moisture and protects hair from thermal damage. Helps cuticle scales nicely overlap and add more shine to hair leaving it smooth, silky and curly. Rich in Pro-Vitamin B5 to retain natural elasticity, Vitamin F to prevent dryness and Almond extract to seal moisture, you are guaranteed lasting and beautiful curls.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply sufficient amount to wet hair and gently massage into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if desired.</p>', '510.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730677', 'DREAMRON CURL PROTECTIVE SHAMPOO ', '', 'DREAMRONCURLPROTECTIVESHAMPOO', 'DREAMRON CURL PROTECTIVE SHAMPOO ', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 14:42:31', 0),
(707, '2228004', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON 2 IN 1 ALOE VERA SHAMPOO ', '', '', '', '', '520.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730066', 'DREAMRON 2 IN 1 ALOE VERA SHAMPOO ', '', 'DREAMRONALOEVERASHAMPOOTWOINONE', 'DREAMRON 2 IN 1 ALOE VERA SHAMPOO ', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 17:11:14', 0),
(708, '2228014', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON 2 IN 1 HENNA SHAMPOO ', '<p>Mildly cleanses hair with natural conditioning agents and is enriched with Vitamin E, Pro-Vitamin B5 and Proteins. It nourishes your hair from root to tip and improves hair growth while strengthening and preventing breakage or damage to hair.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply sufficient amount to wet hair and gently massage into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if desired.</p>', '520.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730097', 'DREAMRON 2 IN 1 HENNA SHAMPOO ', '', 'DREAMRONINHENNASHAMPOOTWOINONE', 'DREAMRON 2 IN 1 HENNA SHAMPOO ', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 17:14:31', 0),
(709, '2228015', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO STRAIGHT PROTECTIVE SHAMPOO ', '<p>An ultra effective formula that protects and nourishes straight hair. The mild SLES free formula cleanses hair while retaining the balance of natural moisture. It overlaps the cuticle scales adding extra shine and preserves its natural elasticity. Rich in Pro-Vitamin B5 and Wheat Proteins it restores cystine that’s depleted in the straightening process and regular maintenance. Biotin (Vitamin H) strengthens hair reducing hair loss, breakage and thermal damage, giving you straight, shiny, cascading hair that’s manageable.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply sufficient amount to wet hair and gently massage into lather. Rinse thoroughly and repeat if desired.</p>', '530.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000733326', 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO STRAIGHT PROTECTIVE SHAMPOO ', '', 'DREAMRONHINUTROSTRAIGHTPROTECTIVESHAMPOO', 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO STRAIGHT PROTECTIVE SHAMPOO ', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 17:25:51', 0),
(710, '2228016', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO COLOR PROTECTIVE SHAMPOO ', '', '', '', '', '530.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730660', 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO COLOR PROTECTIVE SHAMPOO ', '', 'DREAMRONHINUTROCOLORPROTECTIVESHAMPOO', 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO COLOR PROTECTIVE SHAMPOO ', 2, 0, '2020-12-21 17:31:30', 0),
(711, '2228020', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO TREATMENT CONDITIONER', '<p>Specially formulated to treat and restore dry and damaged hair. Enriched with Keratin &amp; Vitamin E to protect against UV damage and preserves natural straightness and elasticity. Transform your hair into a smooth and silky state that is easily manageable.</p>', '', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #222222; font-family: Consolas, \'Lucida Console\', \'Courier New\', monospace; font-size: 12pt; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Apply evenly after shampooing and leave for 2-3 minutes. Rinse well.</span></p>', '550.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730233', 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO TREATMENT CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONHINUTROTREATMENTCONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO TREATMENT CONDITIONER', 2, 0, '2020-12-21 17:33:13', 0),
(712, '2228021', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO INTENSIVE HAIR CONDITIONER', '<p>An intensive conditioning complex that repairs the damage occurred during chemical treatment processes and nourishes hair, back to its naturally healthy state. With Vitamin C & E to neutralize free radicals and shield hair from UV and thermal damage, Jojoba Oil to hydrate hair and Almond Oil to seal moisture, the added conditioning agents safeguard hair color from fading and retain the natural look of your straight or curly hair keeping it healthy and manageable.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply evenly after shampooing and leave for 5-7 minutes. Rinse well.</p>', '550.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730691', 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO INTENSIVE HAIR CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONHINUTROINTENSIVEHAIRCONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON HI-NUTRO INTENSIVE HAIR CONDITIONER', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 17:39:09', 0),
(713, '2228028', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON SUPER CONDITIONER', '<p>The ideal method to minimize damage to hair that has undergone chemical treatments such as perming, straightening or coloring. This unique formula reacts instantly on treated hair closing any opened cuticles, defending it from any further damage. It also removes and neutralizes any alkali treatment residue if present, while locking in the color molecules reducing the fading and enabling a lasting treatment. Rich with conditioning agents like Vitamins, Proteins and UV protectors to keep your hair smooth, shiny and healthy. Recommended only for use after chemical treatment.</p>', '', '', '<p>Just after the chemical treatment (straightening, perming, coloring or bleaching) apply evenly onto the hair and massage gently. To get better result cover the hair by using a polythene cap or a hot towel. Leave for 10 – 15 minutes. Then rinse with running water.</p>', '950.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281997207', 'DREAMRON SUPER CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONSUPERCONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON SUPER CONDITIONER', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 17:52:32', 0),
(714, '2228154', 22, 98, 77, 'DREAMRON KERATIN HAIR THERAPY', '<p>The ideal method to minimize damage to hair that has undergone chemical treatments such as perming, straightening or coloring. This unique formula reacts instantly on treated hair closing any opened cuticles, defending it from any further damage. It also removes and neutralizes any alkali treatment residue if present, while locking in the color molecules reducing the fading and enabling a lasting treatment. Rich with conditioning agents like Vitamins, Proteins and UV protectors to keep your hair smooth, shiny and healthy. Recommended only for use after chemical treatment.</p>', '', '', '<p>Spray sufficient amount on all the length of hair before ironing or blow drying.</p>', '500.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000732404', 'DREAMRON KERATIN HAIR THERAPY', '', 'DREAMRONKERATINHAIRTHERAPY', 'DREAMRON KERATIN HAIR THERAPY', 1, 0, '2020-12-21 18:37:16', 0),
(715, '1120015', 22, 103, 77, 'DREAMRON STRAIGHTENER CREAM', '<p>Frizzy, curly and unmanageable hair is a thing of the past. Choose the hair striaghtener with the most positives. Enriched with Keratin, extra conditioning agents to repair damage, minimize breakage and split ends while giving optimum protection to your hair. Available in both ‘Normal’ & ‘Strong’ types for lasting straight, healthy and beautiful hair.</p>', '', '', '<p>Instruction leaflet with the product should be followed.</p>', '720.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000731605', 'DREAMRON STRAIGHTENER CREAM', '', 'DREAMRONSTRAIGHTENERCREAM', 'DREAMRON STRAIGHTENER CREAM', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 10:42:32', 0),
(716, '2228045', 22, 103, 77, 'DREAMRON HAIR STRAIGHTENER SALON PACK', '<p>Frizzy, curly and unmanageable hair is a thing of the past. Choose the hair striaghtener with the most positives. Enriched with Keratin, extra conditioning agents to repair damage, minimize breakage and split ends while giving optimum protection to your hair. Available in both Strong’ types for lasting straight, healthy and beautiful hair.</p>', '', '', '<p>Instruction leaflet with the product should be followed.</p>', '1150.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000732411', 'DREAMRON HAIR STRAIGHTENER SALON PACK', '', 'DREAMRONHAIRSTRAIGHTENERSALONPACK', 'DREAMRON HAIR STRAIGHTENER SALON PACK', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 10:56:40', 0),
(717, '2228076', 22, 127, 77, 'DREAMRON HAND WASH LEMON', '<p>A highly effective hand wash that will enhance the quality of life by removing all traces of dirt, oil and greasiness while gently cleansing and protecting your hands from germs. Its creamy lather and odor neutralizing fragrance removes pungent odors such as fish, garlic and onion. This pH balanced formula with extra moisturizers will leave your hands feeling soft, smooth and fresh. The attractive colors, scented with a variety of mild fragrances, is suitable for daily use by the whole family and is environmentally friendly. It can be used with all types of water and is available in re-fill pouches.</p>', '', '', '<p>Wet your hands, rub with sufficient amount of handwash &rinse with water.</p>\r\n<p>repeat if desired.</p>', '365.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103417', 'DREAMRON HAND WASH LEMON', '', 'DREAMRONHANDWASHLEMON', 'DREAMRON HAND WASH LEMON', 0, 0, '2020-12-22 11:20:19', 0);
