(720, '2210049', 22, 127, 77, 'DREAMRON ANTIBACTERIAL HAND WASH', '<p>A highly effective hand wash that will enhance the quality of life by removing all traces of dirt, oil and greasiness while gently cleansing and protecting your hands from germs. Its creamy lather and odor neutralizing fragrance removes pungent odors such as fish, garlic and onion. This pH balanced formula with extra moisturizers will leave your hands feeling soft, smooth and fresh. The attractive colors, scented with a variety of mild fragrances, is suitable for daily use by the whole family and is environmentally friendly. It can be used with all types of water and is available in refill pouches.</p>', '', '', '<p>Wet your hands, rub with sufficient amount of handwash &rinse with water.</p>\r\n<p>repeat if desired.</p>', '440.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000737553', 'DREAMRON ANTIBACTERIAL HAND WASH', '', 'DREAMRONANTIBACTERIALHANDWASH', 'DREAMRON ANTIBACTERIAL HAND WASH', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 11:44:42', 0),
(721, '222508', 22, 64, 77, 'DREAMRON DEO-ROLL-ON WOMEN', '<p>An anti-perspirant formula that provides 24 hour protection. Prevents bad odor and wetting while keeping you feeling fresh. Easy application with no visibility after use. The dual attributes (Deodorant + Perfume) take away the need for additional perfume. Available in 12 sensational perfumes.</p>', '', '', '<ul>\r\n<li>Wash and thoroughly dry your armpits.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Roll</strong> on 2–3 swipes of deodorant under each armpit, covering the entire armpit area.</li>\r\n<li>Wait until the product is fully dry before putting your clothes on.</li>\r\n</ul>', '450.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000737003', 'DREAMRON DEO-ROLL-ON ', '', 'DREAMRONDEOROLLON', 'DREAMRON DEO-ROLL-ON ', 3, 0, '2020-12-22 12:12:17', 0),
(722, '2228092', 22, 67, 77, 'DREAMRON DEO-ROLL-ON MEN', '<p>An anti-perspirant formula that provides 24 hour protection. Prevents bad odor and wetting while keeping you feeling fresh. Easy application with no visibility after use. The dual attributes (Deodorant + Perfume) take away the need for additional perfume. Available in 12 sensational perfumes.</p>', '', '', '<ul>\r\n<li>Wash and thoroughly dry your armpits.</li>\r\n<li><strong>Roll</strong> on 2–3 swipes of deodorant under each armpit, covering the entire armpit area.</li>\r\n<li>Wait until the product is fully dry before putting your clothes on.</li>\r\n</ul>', '450.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '', 'DREAMRON DEO-ROLL-ON', '', 'DREAMRONDEOROLLON', 'DREAMRON DEO-ROLL-ON', 6, 0, '2020-12-22 12:18:33', 0),
(723, '22U26KXS76K6', 22, 103, 77, 'DREAMRON WAVING LOTION', '<p>Get lovely, bouncy and perfect curls today. A cold perming solution for natural and permanent curls that stays true till your next hair cut or re-growth. A mild easy to use formula with high quality ingredients which nourish and safeguard the hair to minimize hair damage. Available in both ‘Normal’ & ‘Strong’ types for lasting curl with healthy & beautiful hair.</p>', '', '', '<p>Instruction leaflet with the product should be followed.</p>', '1600.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730325', 'DREAMRON WAVING LOTION', '', 'DREAMRONWAVINGLOTION', 'DREAMRON WAVING LOTION', 6, 0, '2020-12-22 13:27:01', 0),
(724, '2228046', 22, 103, 77, 'DREAMRON HAIR MASCARA', '<p>A range of temporary hair colors that can be applied instantly and be removed with just one wash. Use the MATT color formula to hide the gray and the GLEAM color formula to bring the glitter into your hair.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply on dry or dressed hair and leave it dry or blow dry and comb as you desire. Do not use on eyebrows or eyelashes. Avoid contact with eyes.</p>', '400.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000731612', 'DREAMRON HAIR MASCARA', '', 'DREAMRONHAIRMASCARA', 'DREAMRON HAIR MASCARA', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 15:27:03', 0),
(725, '2228066', 22, 157, 77, 'DREAMRON MIYABI HAIR TREATMENT TONIC', '<p>A nourishing massage tonic that’s a combination of Chamomile, Nettle & Rosemary extracts, Wheat Protein and Vitamins that deep cleanse your hair and scalp leaving it healthy and beautiful. It delivers essential nutrients and oxygen to the hair follicle while strengthening and stimulating hair growth in addition to preventing dryness, reducing dandruff and acting as a mental stress and fatigue reliever.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply a sufficient amount of massage tonic into your head and massage gently with circular movements exerting a light pressure.</p>', '1550.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730578', 'DREAMRON MIYABI HAIR TREATMENT TONIC', '', 'DREAMRONMIYABIHAIRTREATMENTTONIC', 'DREAMRON MIYABI HAIR TREATMENT TONIC', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 15:33:32', 0),
(726, '2228042', 22, 156, 77, 'DREAMRON SILICONE HAIR TREATMENT', '<p>A comprehensive hair treatment with Argan Oil & Vitamin E that enhances the luster of natural or treated hair while giving it a glowing reflection. Tiny Silicone droplets deposit along the hair shaft creating a powerful coating and protects against dryness and damage by replacing lost moisture. It retains treated hair color and gives additional protection to color molecules from UV damage. Protects straightened and permed hair while recovering damage done by chemical treatment processes and other environmental factors, leaving you with smooth, silky, cascading hair.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply to washed, towel dried hair. Distribute evenly in small amount on all the length of the hair.Proceed to set as desired. This can be applied on both damp & dry hair.</p>', '195.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103417', 'DREAMRON SILICONE HAIR TREATMENT', '', 'DREAMRONSILICONEHAIRTREATMENT', 'DREAMRON SILICONE HAIR TREATMENT', 4, 0, '2020-12-22 15:45:25', 0),
(727, '2228171', 22, 156, 77, 'DREAMRON HERBAL MASSAGE TONIC', '<p>A nourishing massage tonic that’s a combination of Chamomile, Nettle &amp; Rosemary extracts, Wheat Protein and Vitamins that deep cleanse your hair and scalp leaving it healthy and beautiful. It delivers essential nutrients and oxygen to the hair follicle while strengthening and stimulating hair growth in addition to preventing dryness, reducing dandruff and acting as a mental stress and fatigue reliever.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply a sufficient amount of massage tonic into your head and massage gently with circular movements exerting a light pressure.</p>', '550.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730837', 'DREAMRON HERBAL MASSAGE TONIC', '', 'DREAMRONHERBALMASSAGETONIC', 'DREAMRON HERBAL MASSAGE TONIC', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 15:58:41', 0),
(728, '2216162', 22, 41, 77, 'DREAMRON KLEARA FACIAL WASH DRY & NORMAL ', '<p>Kleara Facial Wash for Normal / Dry skin retains moisture while cleansing the skin gently. Honey Extract & Sweet Almond Oil helps to avoid dryness and makes the skin younger & healthy.</p>', '', '', '<p>Squeeze a small amount onto your palm and lather. Gently massage the foam on to your wet face with fingers. Rinse thoroughly.</p>', '290.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000736549', 'DREAMRON KLEARA FACIAL WASH DRY & NORMAL', '', 'DREAMRONKLEARAFACIALWASHDRYNORMAL', 'DREAMRON KLEARA FACIAL WASH DRY & NORMAL', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 16:52:12', 0),
(729, '2228067', 22, 41, 77, 'DREAMRON KLEARA FACIAL WASH OILY SKIN ', '<p>Kleara Facial Wash for Oily skin with Orange Fruit Extract cleanses the skin gently while removing excess oils. It gives a refreshing &amp; glowing skin without making it dry.</p>', '', '', '<p>Squeeze a small amount onto your palm and lather. Gently massage the foam on to your wet face with fingers. Rinse thoroughly.</p>', '290.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103417', 'DREAMRON KLEARA FACIAL WASH OILY SKIN', '', 'DREAMRONKLEARAFACIALWASHOILYSKIN', 'DREAMRON KLEARA FACIAL WASH OILY SKIN', 2, 0, '2020-12-22 16:54:58', 0),
(730, '2228165', 22, 106, 77, 'DREAMRON ALGAE DEAD SEA MUD PACK', '<p>Algae Dead Sea Mud Pack absorbs excess oil, clears clogged pores and removes deeply embedded impurities leaving the skin clean &amp;amp; refreshed. Natural minerals and nutrients provided by Dead Sea Mud &amp;amp; Algae help to restore skin elasticity, improve skin texture giving healthy &amp;amp; younger looking skin.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply evenly over the cleansed face &amp;amp; neck avoiding eye area. Allow it to dry for 15-20 minutes. Remove with wet sponge and rinse with water. For better result use once a week.</p>', '520.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000737096', 'DREAMRON ALGAE DEAD SEA MUD PACK', '', 'DREAMRONALGAEDEADSEAMUDPACK', 'DREAMRON ALGAE DEAD SEA MUD PACK', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 17:13:16', 0),
(731, '2228175', 22, 106, 77, 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACIAL PACK', '<p>The Algae Facial Pack cleanses the skin well, firms &amp; tightens the facial tissues. It avoids appearance of pimples, blackheads, whiteheads and minimizes formation of skin wrinkles and fine lines. Algae and fruit extracts nourishes, re-hydrate and rejuvenate the skin leaving it moist, fair &amp; healthy.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply evenly over the cleansed face &amp; neck avoiding eye area. Allow it to dry for 15-20 minutes. Remove with wet sponge and rinse with water. For better result use once a week.</p>', '470.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000737102', 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACIAL PACK', '', 'DREAMRONALGAEFACIALPACK', 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACIAL PACK', 2, 0, '2020-12-22 17:17:53', 0),
(732, '2228167', 22, 45, 77, 'DREAMRON ALGAE CLEANSING MILK', '<p>A combination of deep cleansing agents that dissolve embedded dirt, excess oil, sebum and make-up trapped within skin pores. The highly nutritious Algae extract nourishes while the pH balanced formula refreshes skin maintaining its natural balances. With added moisturizers to prevent dryness and leave you with clean and healthy skin.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply all over the face & neck and massage gently using fingertips with circular motions. Wipe off with a damp cotton wool. Rinse with water if required. Finally use Algae Skin Toner.</p>', '325.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000737072', 'DREAMRON ALGAE CLEANSING MILK', '', 'DREAMRONALGAECLEANSINGMILK', 'DREAMRON ALGAE CLEANSING MILK', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 17:20:43', 0),
(733, '2228174', 22, 48, 77, 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACIAL SCRUB', '<p>The Algae Facial Scrub gently removes dead cells, dirt and grime while the Walnut and Apricot shell deep cleans and stimulates fresh skin cells. Natural minerals and nutrients, nourish and moisturize your skin improving its complexion and glow. For healthy, soft skin without blemishes, blackheads or whiteheads.</p>', '', '', '<p>Moisten the face &amp; neck, apply with wet fingertips and massage gently with upward circular motions avoiding eye area. Rinse well and pat dry. Apply Toner &amp; moisturizer as usual.</p>', '410.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000737133', 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACIAL SCRUB', '', 'DREAMRONALGAEFACIALSCRUB', 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACIAL SCRUB', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 17:24:25', 0),
(734, '2228177', 22, 108, 77, 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACE MOISTURIZER', '<p>The mild &amp; non-greasy Algae Face Moisturizer maintains skin’s moisture balance. Its restructuring benefits and Algae Extract leave the skin smooth, soft &amp; supple. It makes skin resilient to damaging effects on the environment.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply all over the face &amp; neck with gentle upward strokes. This is ideal to use before applying make-ups. For better results use twice a day.</p>', '405.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103417', 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACE MOISTURIZER', '', 'DREAMRONALGAEFACEMOISTURIZER', 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACE MOISTURIZER', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 17:27:29', 0),
(735, '2228163', 22, 108, 77, 'DREAMRON ALGAE ANTI-ACNE CREAM', '<p>Developed to a special herbal formula that acts against the formation of acne. It dissolves sebum that is clogged in pores and slows the proliferation of bacteria, leaving your skin healthy, smooth and radiant. With added moisturizers to improve skin texture it also stimulates the reorganization of new skin fibers while healing to prevent permanent scar marks.</p>', '', '', '<p>Cleans the face with Algae Cleansing Milk and apply a sufficient amount of Anti-Acne Cream over the affected area. Use twice a day. For better results use twice a day.</p>', '415.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000737058', 'DREAMRON ALGAE ANTI-ACNE CREAM', '', 'DREAMRONALGAEANTIACNECREAM', 'DREAMRON ALGAE ANTI-ACNE CREAM', 2, 2, '2020-12-22 17:29:43', 0),
(736, '2238166', 22, 104, 77, 'DREAMRON ALGAE SKIN TONER', '<p>Dreamron Algae Skin Toner Naturally tones the skin with natural astringentGive refreshing and soothing the skin.improve skin texture giving healthy & younger looking skin.It removes final residues,impurities and makes skin pores appear small & maintain moisture and oil balance.</p>', '', '', '<p><span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Apply all over the<strong> </strong></span>face<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> & neck and massage gently using fingertips with circular motions. Wipe off with a damp cotton wool. Rinse with water if required. Finally use </span>Algae Skin Toner<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">.</span></p>', '295.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000737065', 'DREAMRON ALGAE SKIN TONER', '', 'DREAMRONALGAESKINTONER', 'DREAMRON ALGAE SKIN TONER', 0, 0, '2020-12-22 17:35:19', 0),
(737, '2228040', 22, 91, 77, 'DREAMRON LEAVE ON CONDITIONER', '<p>Dreamron Leave On Conditioner is light weight formula that infuses moisture into hair fibers giving a shiny, frizz free &amp; manageable hair. Added Keratin and Argan Oil repairs the hair damages and improve the smoothness while Vitamin E protects the hair leaving it healthy.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply sufficient amount to all over the hair shaft. Directly style your hair as desired. Do not rinse.</p>', '850.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000736082', 'DREAMRON LEAVE ON CONDITIONER', '', 'DREAMRONLEAVEONCONDITIONER', 'DREAMRON LEAVE ON CONDITIONER', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 17:40:22', 0),
(738, '2228029', 22, 90, 77, 'DREAMRON SCALP PROTECTIVE EMULSION', '<p>An unique combination of oil free formula that protects your scalp from external damages caused by chemical treatments such as perming, straightening or coloring. Mild ingredients such as Keratin and other anti-irritant agents help safeguard the scalp by forming a protective film over while preventing dryness caused by the chemical treatments.</p>', '', '', '<p>Get sufficient amount to your fingertips and apply evenly on your scalp & hairline before chemical treatment (perming, straightening, coloring & bleaching) For professional use only.</p>', '199.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000730493', 'DREAMRON SCALP PROTECTIVE EMULSION', '', 'DREAMRONSCALPPROTECTIVEEMULSION', 'DREAMRON SCALP PROTECTIVE EMULSION', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 17:47:47', 0),
(739, '2201196', 22, 122, 70, 'DREAMRON ALGAE BODY BUTTER', '<p><span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">Added </span>Shea Butter<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> & </span>Cocoa Butter<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> are skin conditioning agents that give better conditioning ability to the skin and help to prevent excess dryness of the skin, making it soft & smooth. Containing </span>Algae<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> Extract nourishes & strengthens the skin leaving it healthy & beautiful.</span></p>', '', '', '<p>Massage into the skin using figertips with circular motions.</p>', '550.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000737164', 'DREAMRON ALGAE BODY BUTTER', '', 'DREAMRONALGAEBODYBUTTER', 'DREAMRON ALGAE BODY BUTTER', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 17:53:55', 0),
(740, '2228068', 22, 106, 77, 'DREAMRON KLEARA ROTORUA MUD PACK', '<p>Kleara Facial Pack for oily skin gently cleanse your skin, absorb excess oil, remove blackheads and clear clogged pores while moisturizing and softening. Added Rotorua Mud detoxifies and purify while nourishing the skin with natural rejuvenating minerals leaving it softer and more radiant appearance.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply evenly over the cleansed face &amp; neck avoiding eye area. Allow it to dry for 15-20 minutes. Remove with wet sponge and rinse with water. For better result use once a week.</p>', '980.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000736488', 'DREAMRON KLEARA ROTORUA MUD PACK', '', 'DREAMRONKLEARAROTORUAMUDPACK', 'DREAMRON KLEARA ROTORUA MUD PACK', 0, 0, '2020-12-22 17:56:41', 0),
(741, '2228164', 22, 108, 77, 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACE MASSAGE GEL', '<p>The active ingredients Vitamin E beads and Algae extract penetrate skin and directly delivers all its nutritional benefits while massaging and improving the skin texture. It restores moisture and revives the natural radiance and smoothness of your skin.</p>', '', '', '<p>Apply<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> Algae </span>Face Massage Gel<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> on the </span>face<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> & neck. Gently </span>massage<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> for 15-20 minutes </span>using<span style=\"color: #202124; font-family: arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\"> upward and outward strokes. Leave for 5 minutes. Remove with moist cotton wool or rinse with water.</span></p>', '505.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4796000736921', 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACE MASSAGE GEL', '', 'DREAMRONALGAEFACEMASSAGEGEL', 'DREAMRON ALGAE FACE MASSAGE GEL', 1, 0, '2020-12-22 18:05:03', 0),
