(779, '5501072', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE EMERY BOARDS - 1078', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Coarse / fine</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Strong & flexible for easy filing</li>\r\n<li>Convenient size perfect for travel</li>\r\n<li>Contains 10 high-quality boards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Hold the emery board at a 45-degree angle under your nail edge. Begin with the coarse side to shape and use the finer side to smooth off nail edges.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Basicare also provides you more products to keep nails with a healthy and beautiful look:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Cuticle stick- to keep your cuticle smooth and neat.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Nail buffer- for a healthy and natural shine</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\"> </p>', '', '', '<p>Remove nail enamel before filing. To prevent nails from peeling, file with dry nails. Always start at the side of the nail and file toward the middle. File in one direction to prevent splitting. Do not “saw” back and forth.</p>', '270.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125910787', 'BASICARE EMERY BOARDS - 1078', '', 'BASICAREEMERYBOARDS', 'BASICARE EMERY BOARDS - 1078', 1, 0, '2020-12-24 17:51:32', 0),
(780, '5501025', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE EMERY BOARDS - 1077', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Coarse / fine</li>\r\n<li>Strong & flexible for easy filing</li>\r\n<li>Convenient size perfect for travel</li>\r\n<li>Contains 10 high-quality boards</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Hold the emery board at a 45-degree angle under your nail edge. Begin with the coarse side to shape and use the finer side to smooth off nail edges.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Basicare also provides you more products to keep nails with a healthy and beautiful look:</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Cuticle stick- to keep your cuticle smooth and neat.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Nail buffer- for a healthy and natural shine</p>', '', '', '<p>Remove nail enamel before filing. To prevent nails from peeling, file with dry nails. Always start at the side of the nail and file toward the middle. File in one direction to prevent splitting. Do not “saw” back and forth.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '230.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125910770', 'BASICARE EMERY BOARDS - 1077', '', 'BASICAREEMERYBOARDS', 'BASICARE EMERY BOARDS - 1077', 1, 0, '2020-12-24 17:54:56', 0),
(781, '5501101', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE NAIL CLEANSING BRUSH - 1170', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Essential for manicure</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Comfortable easy-to-grip handel</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Hygenic nylon bristles & plastic handel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Germs are often invisible to your naked eyes. It is essential to have a good grooming tool for effective cleaning on your hands. Made of the plastic handle and soft nylon bristles for a hygienic purpose, this nail brush is specially designed to remove dirt and bacteria hide under and around your fingernails. It exfoliates and stimulates your cuticles, leaving your fingers fresh and healthy looking. Use with your favorite hand soap.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Care: gently wash the brush in mild soapy water. Rinse thoroughly after use and pat on a dry towel for excess water. Hang to dry in an airy place.</p>', '', '', '', '460.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125911708', 'BASICARE NAIL CLEANSING BRUSH - 1170', '', 'BASICARENAILCLEANSINGBRUSH', 'BASICARE NAIL CLEANSING BRUSH - 1170', 1, 0, '2020-12-24 18:01:23', 0),
(782, '5501177', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE BABY NAIL KIT - 1241', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Chrome plated nail clipper</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Sapphire nail file w/safety blade</span></li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Soft grip safety scissor</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Trimming babies’ nails with an improper tool is risky. This baby nail kit is specially designed for grooming your babies to nail safely. The contoured blades of nail clipper trim nails safely and easily. Lever-action works comfortably with your either hand. For smaller nails & toenails safely scissor with blunt tips will give you the best control without applying any pressure to nail beds. After trimming nails. Smooth-off the rough edge with the sapphire nail file. Our sapphire nail file is specially designed with extra fine grit and round tip. It is safe for babies sensitive nails.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\"> </p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Care: clean blades after each use. Use a bristle brush to remove residue from the nail file. To prevent rusting, have the nail clipper and nail file slight oiled and kept in a dry place.</span></p>\r\n<p> </p>', '', '', '', '820.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125912415', 'BASICARE BABY NAIL KIT - 1241', '', 'BASICAREBABYNAILKIT', 'BASICARE BABY NAIL KIT - 1241', 1, 0, '2020-12-24 18:10:36', 0),
(783, '5501108', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE NAIL BRUSH WITH PUMICE STONE - 2131', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Volcano pumice stone</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Natural wood & bristles</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Smoothes out callous area</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">This lightweight, porous pumice atone with abrasive characters make it perfect tool to smooth out callous areas of feet, toes, hands, elbows, knees and other areas of the body. It gently removes dead skin cells and reveals young healthy skin. Use pumice stone in the shower or moisten the stone prior to use. Do not use the stone if the skin is not wet. Rub firmly over the callous area in a circular motion to remove dead skin. Apply your favorite skin lotion or cream to moisturize the treated area.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Germs are often invisible to your naked eyes. It is essential to have a good grooming tool for effective cleaning on your nails. Made of natural wood and bristles, this nail brush is specially designed to remove dirt and bacteria hide under and around your nails. It exfoliates and stimulates your cuticles, leaving your hands fresh and healthy looking. Use with your favorite hand soap.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Care: rinse the stone and wash the brush with warm water after each use. Hang on to dry in an airy place.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Cautions: consult your doctor prior to use if you have diabetes or circulatory impairment problem. Do not use if the area to be treated is wounded or scratched. Do not use on any redness or inflammation in the area to be treated.</p>', '', '', '', '500.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125921318', 'BASICARE NAIL BRUSH WITH PUMICE STONE - 2131', '', 'BASICARENAILBRUSHWITHPUMICESTONE', 'BASICARE NAIL BRUSH WITH PUMICE STONE - 2131', 1, 0, '2020-12-24 18:14:15', 0),
(784, '5501087', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE 4 - WAY NAIL BUFFER BLOCK - 1109', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">4 functions in 1 – file, remove, polish & buff</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Perfect for travel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">This cushioned buffer with 4 functions in one perfect follows the curve of nail and makes polish fast and easy. Simply files, polishes, and buffs as following 4 steps and leaving nails a salon shine.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\"> </p>', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">Step 1: file</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">File nail in one direction to shape edges and remove ridges.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">Step 2: remove</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">Remove ridges across to have a fine even finish.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">Step 3: buff</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">Polish across nail in one direction to have a fine smooth finish.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">Step 4: polish</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">Buff across nail in one direction until as shiny as desired.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">remove nail enamel before buffing. Over buff with step 1 and 2 might weaken your nails. Step 4 can be repeated as often as you wish.</p>', '430.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281997207', 'BASICARE 4 - WAY NAIL BUFFER BLOCK - 1109', '', 'BASICAREWAYNAILBUFFERBLOCK', 'BASICARE 4 - WAY NAIL BUFFER BLOCK - 1109', 2, 0, '2020-12-24 18:18:20', 0),
(785, '5501022', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE SAPPHIRE NAIL FILE - 1072', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Harden steel blade for long lasting</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">For sharping/ smoothing</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Convenient compact size</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">This sapphire nail file is precision crafted and fully inspected to help prevent nails from cracking and splitting. Perfect for shaping and smoothing.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\"> </p>', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">file your nails when dry to ensure smoother edges. Always file in one direction. Back and forth filing may cause cracking and splitting. Keep out of reach of children. This product is not intended for use by children.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">Care: use a bristle brush to remove residue.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '310.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125910725', 'BASICARE SAPPHIRE NAIL FILE - 1072', '', 'BASICARESAPPHIRENAILFILE', 'BASICARE SAPPHIRE NAIL FILE - 1072', 1, 0, '2020-12-24 18:54:11', 0),
(786, '5501024', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE CUTICLE TRIMMER - 1076', '', '', '', '', '390.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '8719281103486', 'BASICARE CUTICLE TRIMMER - 1076', '', 'BASICARECUTICLETRIMMER', 'BASICARE CUTICLE TRIMMER - 1076', 1, 0, '2020-12-25 15:09:16', 0),
(787, '5501071', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE CUTICLE STICKS - 1075', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Slant / point – 10 pcs per pack</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Pushing back cuticles & cleaning under nails</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Made from natural wood, these cuticle sticks are selected from sustainable sources and specially designed for manicure care purpose. The wooden cuticle stick is a better alternative to plastic or metal cuticle sticks, which can be too harsh to the nail bed.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\"> </p>', '', '', '<p>After applying your favorite cuticle remover, hold this wooden cuticle stick like a pen and use the slant end to gently push back the cuticles. Move the sticks in circles around the nail bed to remove dead skin. Clean under nails with a pointed end. After pushing back cuticles, trim remaining hangnails with our <strong>cuticle products: cuticle scissors cuticle nippers cuticle clippers cuticle trimmer</strong></p>\r\n<p><strong> </strong></p>', '310.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125910756', 'CUTICLE STICKS - 1075', '', 'CUTICLESTICKS', 'CUTICLE STICKS - 1075', 0, 0, '2020-12-25 15:15:17', 0),
(788, '5501094', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE SILICON CARBIDE PEDICURE FILE - 1141', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Proficiently remove callus & hard skin</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Safe & easy to use</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">This foot rasp is specially designed to eliminate calluses and hardened skin on your hands and feet. It is safe and easy to use.</p>', '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">It is best to use on moist skin. Simply soak the affected area in warm water to soften skin. Start with foot rasp. Work back & forth with a press pull motion. Smooth off with pedicure file. Follow up with up with your favorite lotion.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.25in;\">Care: clean rasp after each use. To prevent rusting, have the rasp lightly oiled and kept in a dry place. Diabetics should contact a doctor before using this product. Keep out of reach of children.</p>\r\n<p> </p>', '580.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125911418', 'BASICARE SILICON CARBIDE PEDICURE FILE - 1141', '', 'BASICARESILICONCARBIDEPEDICUREFILE', 'BASICARE SILICON CARBIDE PEDICURE FILE - 1141', 0, 0, '2020-12-25 15:26:33', 0),
(789, '5501028', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE TOE SEPARATORS - 1094', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">For nail polish application & pedicure</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">2 separators per package</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">These toe separators are specially designed to help application of nail polish without smudging on the skin and to help with a pedicure. Simply place toe separators between toes and remove when nail polish is completely dry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Care: gently wash the toe separators in warm soapy water. Rinse thoroughly and squeeze for excess water. Allow it to air dry.</p>', '', '', '', '310.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125910947', 'BASICARE TOE SEPARATORS - 1094', '', 'BASICARETOESEPARATORS', 'BASICARE TOE SEPARATORS - 1094', 1, 0, '2020-12-25 15:47:34', 0),
(790, '5501006', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE MANICURE TOOL KIT - 1017', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Nail clipper/tweezers/toenail clipper/ sapphire nail file</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">All in a carrying pouch/perfect for travel</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Nail clipper – to trim nails quick and easy.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Tweezers – for quick and easy hair removal.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Toenail clipper – makes trimming toenails fast and easy!</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Sapphire nail file – smoothes off the edge of nails to help prevent cracking or breaking.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Care: clean blades/tips after each use. To prevent rusting have your tools slightly oiled and kept in a dry place. Keep out of reach of children.</p>', '', '', '', '1190.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125910176', 'BASICARE MANICURE TOOL KIT - 1017', '', 'BASICAREMANICURETOOLKIT', 'BASICARE MANICURE TOOL KIT - 1017', 1, 0, '2020-12-25 15:51:29', 0),
(791, '5501131', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE COMPACT MANICURE KIT - 3106', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #333333; background: white;\">It\'s time you pamper your hands and nails. Packaged in duo-zippered accessible pouch, these beautifully designed long lasting tools are made to give you rejuvenating and indulging Spa treatment </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #333333; background: white;\">Cuticle Scissors: Its stainless steel extra fine curved blades minutely trims the dead skin that develops around the base of nail bed, the cuticle.</span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #333333; background: white;\"><span style=\"mso-spacerun: yes;\"> </span>Sapphire Nail File: Precisely constructed hardened steel blade shapes the edges of nails and smoothes out the calluses. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #333333; background: white;\">Nail Clippers: Provided with non-slip handle, its contoured blades trims the rough edges of nails thereby shaping them in the desired shapes. </span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-family: \'Arial\',\'sans-serif\'; color: #333333; background: white;\">Tweezers: Its perfectly structured slant tips helps remove splinters and stray hairs on your hairs.</span></p>', '', '', '', '1390.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125931065', 'BASICARE COMPACT MANICURE KIT - 3106', '', 'BASICARECOMPACTMANICUREKIT', 'BASICARE COMPACT MANICURE KIT - 3106', 2, 0, '2020-12-25 15:56:25', 0),
(792, '5501047', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE TOENAIL CLIPPER -1030', '<ul>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Contoured blades with laser file & catcher</li>\r\n<li class=\"MsoNormal\">Unique non-slip handle design</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Contoured blades trim toenails safely and easily without pulling or learning. After trimming your toenails, smooth off the rough edge with laser file. Then, have a healthy and natural shine on nails with our nail buffer. Simply slide back the catcher to empty nails after trimming is completed.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Care: clean blades after each use. To prevent rusting have your tools slightly oiled and kept in a dry place. Keep out of reach of children.</p>', '', '', '', '420.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125910305', 'BASICARE TOENAIL CLIPPER -1030', '', 'BASICARETOENAILCLIPPER', 'BASICARE TOENAIL CLIPPER -1030', 2, 0, '2020-12-25 16:00:23', 0),
(793, '5501008', 22, 84, 79, 'BASICARE NAIL CLIPPER - 1026', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Contoured slant blades with laser file</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Trim nails easily & safely</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Compact size fits into your bag easily. Contoured blades trim nails safely and easily. Lever-action works comfortably your nails, smooth off the rough edge with laser file. Then, have a healthy and natural shine on nails with our nail buffer.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: .25in;\">Care: clean blades after each use. To prevent rusting have your tools slightly oiled and kept in a dry place. Keep out of reach of children.</p>', '', '', '', '380.00', '0.00', 6, 1, '4895125910268', 'BASICARE NAIL CLIPPER - 1026', '', 'BASICARENAILCLIPPER', 'BASICARE NAIL CLIPPER - 1026', 2, 0, '2020-12-25 16:05:42', 0),
