(801, 'DAX-SN', 23, 235, 10, 'Dax super - neat hair cream wax 99g', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; padding-left: 30px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Soybean Oil</strong> — Natural conditioner and antioxidant. Locks in moisture to make hair stronger and more manageable.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Carrot Root Extract</strong> — Natural antioxidant.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Beta Carotene</strong> — Conditions hair helping to maintain normal hair growth.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Vitamin E</strong> — Helps prevent split ends and aids in hair growth. Helps to reduce dryness and adds shine. Antioxidant.</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\">For a soft, natural look</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px;\">Medium hold for all types of styles</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 10px 0px;\">Best used on short to medium-length hair</li>\r\n</ul>', 'DAX Super Neat is a conditioning hair cream that offers a light hold. It’s great for many hair types and styles.', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Raleway, sans-serif;\">Petrolatum, Cetearyl Alcohol, PEG-150 Stearate, Steareth-20, Oleth-5, Microcrystalline Wax 1275, Fragrance (Parfum), Glycine Soja (Soybean) Oil, Beta-Carotene (CI 40800), Tocopheryl Acetate, Linalool, Butylphenyl Methylpropional, Benzyl Benzoate, Citronellol, Hexylcinnamicaldehyde, Hydroxycitronellol, Benzyl Salicylate, Amyl Cinnamal</span></p>', '<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; list-style-position: initial; list-style-image: initial; padding-left: 30px; font-family: Raleway, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 10px;\">Place desired amount between palms and rub. Apply to clean damp or dry hair. Style with fingertips until desired look is achieved.</li>\r\n</ul>', '1190.00', '0.00', 6, 99, '', 'Dax super - neat hair cream wax 99g', '', 'haircream', 'Dax super - neat hair cream wax 99g', 24, 18, '2021-01-04 17:31:45', 0),
(802, '071249207277', 23, 90, 23, 'L\'Oreal Advanced Haircare Color Vibrancy Nourishing Shampoo', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Anti-fade, high shine & protects. Color treated hair. New look. Up to 60 days vibrancy with system. The Science of Colored Hair: Color-processing can make the fiber porous and fragile. Color fades and loses vibrancy. Chemically treated hair needs to be nourished and protected. Our expert protecting formula. With linseed elixir + anti oxidants [uv]. Tested Results: Up to 60 days vibrancy + instantly nourished. Anti-fade, high shine and fiber protection.</span></p>', '', '<p><span style=\"font-family: Montserrat, sans-serif;\">Aqua/Water/Eau, Sodium Laureth Sulfate, Coco-Betaine, Sodium Chloride, Glycol Distearate, Dimethicone, Parfum/Fragrance, Sodium Benzoate, Hexylene Glycol, Cocamide Mipa, Salicylic Acid, Carbomer, Ethylhexyl Methoxycinnamate, Guar Hydroxypropyltrimonium Chloride, Arginine, Glutamic Acid, Linalool, Niacinamide, Tocopherol, Disodium EDTA, Benzophenone-4, Benzyl Salicylate, Benzyl Alcohol, Serine, Hydroxypropyltrimonium Hydrolyzed Wheat Protein, Limonene, Amyl Cinnamal, Coumarin, Citronellol, Poly(Linseed Oil), Alpha-Isomethyl Ionone, Fumaric Acid, Phenoxyethanol, BHT, Sodium Hydroxide, Citric Acid.</span></p>', '', '1890.00', '0.00', 6, 250, '', 'L\'Oreal Advanced Haircare Color Vibrancy Nourishing Shampoo', '', 'ColorVibrancyNourishingShampoo', 'L\'Oreal Advanced Haircare Color Vibrancy Nourishing Shampoo', 3, 0, '2021-01-08 15:27:22', 0),
(803, '071249383612', 23, 90, 23, 'L\'Oreal Paris Elvive Dream Lengths Restoring Shampoo', '<ul class=\"a-unordered-list a-vertical a-spacing-mini\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 0px 18px; color: #111111; padding: 0px; font-family: \'Amazon Ember\', Arial, sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"> </li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Use the full Dream lengths system for your long hair care routine. Massage Dream Lengths Shampoo on wet hair. Lather. Rinse. Then follow with Dream Lengths Conditioner and No Haircut Cream Leave In Conditioner</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; list-style: disc; overflow-wrap: break-word; margin: 0px;\"><span class=\"a-list-item\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Dream Lengths has a sweet candy fragrance with notes of pomegranate, caramel orchid and milk sorbet, making it irresistible and indulgent.</span></li>\r\n</ul>', 'Long hair? Help seal split ends in just 1 use with Elvive Dream Lengths formulated with fine castor oil and vitamins B3 and B5\r\nStrengthen hair\'s length and help seal split ends with Elvive Dream Lengths Shampoo, Conditioner and No Haircut Cream Leave In Conditioner\r\nParaben-free Creamy Restoring Shampoo visibly repairs damage without weigh down, adds shine, Protects lengths and strengthens', '', '', '1950.00', '0.00', 6, 250, '', 'L\'Oreal Paris Elvive Dream Lengths Restoring Shampoo', '', 'DreamLengthsRestoringShampoo', 'L\'Oreal Paris Elvive Dream Lengths Restoring Shampoo', 2, 0, '2021-01-08 17:24:21', 0),
